NK011(da)003:0: rdo rje phur bu rong lugs kyi las byang dngos
NK011(da)003:1: grub rgya mtsho'i snying po zhes bya ba bzhugs so
NK011(da)003:2: // na mo gu ru badz+ra ku m+aa r+aa ya /
NK011(da)003:3: chos kun ka dag rig pa'i nyin byed dbang //
NK011(da)003:4: sgrib gnyis chu 'dzin las grol 'gyur med kyi //
NK011(da)003:5: bde chen rdo rje'i don gzigs bla ma dang //
NK011(da)003:6: dpal chen phur pa'i dkyil 'khor 'khor lor 'dud //
NK011(da)003:7: gang gi sgrub thabs mkhas pa rong zom lugs //
NK011(da)003:8: las byang 'bring po blo gros rgyal mtshan gyis //
NK011(da)003:9: legs bshad dngos grub rgya mtsho zhes grags pa //
NK011(da)003:10: snying por dril ba'i yi ge 'di na spel //
NK011(da)003:11: dbang thob cing dam tshig la gnas pa'i sngags pas
NK011(da)003:12: mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i gnas khang mdzes par brgyan
NK011(da)003:13: / lha phur dang bsnyen phur sogs rten dang mchod
NK011(da)003:14: gtor sman raka giis mtshon nyer mkho'i yo byad thams
NK011(da)003:15: cad tshogs par bshams nas rnal 'byor la 'jug par
NK011(da)003:16: / bya'o // de la sngon 'gro dngos gzhi rjes kyi bya ba dang gsum las /
NK011(da)003:18: bka' bsgo mtshams gcod tshogs bsags dang //
NK011(da)003:19: dam bca' byin dbab mchod byin brlab //
NK011(da)003:20: ces pa'i dang po bka' bsgob ni /
NK011(da)003:21: skyabs sems dang rol mos byin dbab pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK011(da)003:22: bdag nyid skad cig gis dpal chen rdo rje gzhon
NK011(da)003:23: nu yum dang bcas pa'i skur gyur pa'i snyems pas
NK011(da)003:25: nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
NK011(da)003:26: nga yi bka' las 'da' ma byed //
NK011(da)003:27: rdo rje gsang ba'i bka' las ni //
NK011(da)003:28: sdig can gang zhig 'da' byed pa //
NK011(da)003:29: stobs chen khro bo chen po yis //
NK011(da)003:30: klad pa tshal pa brgya ru khos //
NK011(da)003:33: gri h+na p+aa ya gri h+na p+aa ya h+aum /
NK011(da)003:34: +aa na ya hoh b+ha ga w+aan bid+ya r+aa dza ya h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:35: gnyis pa mtshams bcad pa ni /
NK011(da)003:36: rang nyid khro bo gnod mdzes rdo rje tho ba dang lcags kyu 'dzin par bskyed la /
NK011(da)003:39: thugs ka nas me dmar po 'phros /
NK011(da)003:41: zhes pas nyi ma'i gdan du gyur /
NK011(da)003:42: sh+r+ai h+aum k+aa ra badz+ra man+da la h'u phata /
NK011(da)003:44: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor dbus su ni //
NK011(da)003:45: dbyar gyi char sprin lta bu'i mdog /
NK011(da)003:46: bskal pa'i me dpung bzhin du 'bar //
NK011(da)003:47: dor stabs tshul du zhabs bgrad cing //
NK011(da)003:48: smin mtshams khro gnyer 'bar ba can //
NK011(da)003:49: zhal gsum mche gtsigs rnam par gyur //
NK011(da)003:50: phyag gnyis h+aum gi rgya bcings nas //
NK011(da)003:51: rdo rje dang ni dril bu dang //
NK011(da)003:52: g.yas gnyis lcags kyu ral gri dang //
NK011(da)003:53: g.yon gnyis dgra s+t+wa zhags pa bsnams //
NK011(da)003:54: bsgo ba'i bka' rnams nyan par byos //
NK011(da)003:56: khro bo rdo rje gnod mdzes kyis h+aum k+aa ra
NK011(da)003:57: la phyogs bcur khro bcu'i gdan bshams pa'i bka' bsgos
NK011(da)003:58: te thugs ka nas tho ba dang lcags kyu spros
NK011(da)003:59: te h'u k+aa ra la gtad par bsam /
NK011(da)003:60: sh+r+ai h'u tak+ki r+aa dza badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+ha h'u phata /
NK011(da)003:61: 'dod rgyal sngo skya g.yas dkar g.yon dmar zhal //
NK011(da)003:62: phyag drug dang po rang gi phyag rgya bcings //
NK011(da)003:63: bar pa gnyis kyis lcags kyu zhags pa dang //
NK011(da)003:64: phyag g.yas tha ma mda' gzhu 'dzin la brtson //
NK011(da)003:65: phyag g.yon tha ma nyi ma'i gdan bsnams gyur //
NK011(da)003:68: 'dod rgyal gyi thugs ka nas ma bcu phyogs bcur 'phros pas nyi ma'i gdan bcur gyur /
NK011(da)003:70: khro bo'i rgyal po 'di dag ni //
NK011(da)003:71: bgegs kyi tshogs rnams kun nas bshig /
NK011(da)003:72: blo ldan rab tu sbyar ba yi //
NK011(da)003:73: cho ga bzhin du phur bus gdab //
NK011(da)003:75: khro bo 'dod pa'i rgyal pos phyogs bcur phyin te
NK011(da)003:76: phyogs skyong bcu lcags kyus bzung tho bas brdungs te
NK011(da)003:77: phyogs bcu'i nyi gdan gyi steng du bsnol nas bzhag
NK011(da)003:79: gdan steng khro rgyal chen po rnams //
NK011(da)003:80: zhe sdang rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK011(da)003:81: khro chen rngams brjid sprul pa'i sku //
NK011(da)003:82: nyi ma'i gdan la bzhugs su gsol //
NK011(da)003:84: so so'i gdan steng du 'khod pa 'od du zhu ba las /
NK011(da)003:86: bgegs 'dul khro rgyal bcu po ni //
NK011(da)003:87: phyogs bcu'i dkyil 'khor phyogs mtshams su //
NK011(da)003:88: rim pa bzhin du kun tu 'khod //
NK011(da)003:89: bgegs rnams thams cad bshig pa'i phyir //
NK011(da)003:90: gnod mdzes bka' byung phur bus btab //
NK011(da)003:91: g+ha g+ha g+h+aa ta ya g+h+aa ta ya /
NK011(da)003:97: badz+ra ki la ya badz+ra d+ha r+aa any+dz+aa pa ya
NK011(da)003:98: ti sarba big+h+nam k+aa ya w+aa k+tsi t+ta badz+ra k+ai
NK011(da)003:101: 'jigs byed khro rgyal chen po bcu //
NK011(da)003:102: rdo rje phur bu nyid byas pa //
NK011(da)003:105: sku smad phur bu 'bar ba la //
NK011(da)003:106: sku stod khro bo chen po ste //
NK011(da)003:107: zhal gsum pa la phyag drug pa //
NK011(da)003:108: bgegs kyi tshogs rnams mgo ru gzir //
NK011(da)003:109: badz+ra kro d+ha h'u k+aa ra h'u gardza gardza h'u phata /
NK011(da)003:110: badz+ra kro d+ha bi dza ya h+aum ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:111: badz+ra kro d+ha n+ai la dan+da h+aum da ha da ha h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:112: badz+ra kro d+ha ya m+aan+ta ka h+aum pa tsa pa tsa h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:113: badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la h+aum b+han+d+ha b+han+d+ha h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:114: badz+ra kro d+ha ha ya g+r+ai ba h+aum hu lu hu lu h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:115: badz+ra kro d+ha a pa r+aa dzi ta h+aum tish+tha tish+tha h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:116: badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da li h+aum ts+tshin+d+ha ts+tshin+d+ha h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:117: badz+ra kro d+ha tree lo kya bi dza ya h+aum b+hin+d+ha b+hin+d+ha h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:118: badz+ra kro d+ha ma h+aa ba la h+aum s+pho ta s+pho ta h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:120: g+ha g+ha g+h+aa ta ya g+h+aa ta ya /
NK011(da)003:126: badz+ra k+ai la ya badz+ra d+ha r+aa adz+ny+aa pa ya
NK011(da)003:127: ti sarba big+h+n+aam k+aa ya w+aa k+tsit+ta badz+ra k+ai la
NK011(da)003:129: de nas khro bo rnams rim pa bzhin phyogs bcu'i
NK011(da)003:130: phyogs skyong rnams kyi snying gar babs pas lus phug
NK011(da)003:131: ste 'og gi nyi ma'i gdan la sbrags par bsam
NK011(da)003:133: phyogs bzhi mtshams bzhi steng 'og bcu'i //
NK011(da)003:134: bdud 'dul khro rgyal chen po rnams //
NK011(da)003:135: kun kyang zhal gsum phyag drug ste //
NK011(da)003:136: ya mtshan che ba'i dbu rgyan can //
NK011(da)003:137: dbu skra kham nag ral pa ni //
NK011(da)003:139: spyan dmar glog stong 'gyu ba bzhin //
NK011(da)003:140: mche ba zangs yag rnon po gtsigs //
NK011(da)003:141: rkan sgra gtogs pas khams gsum 'khrugs //
NK011(da)003:142: bdud rgyal rnams kyis zhabs la btud //
NK011(da)003:143: mdzes pa'i lha mo mang po yis //
NK011(da)003:144: snyan pa'i glu dbyangs du mas bstod //
NK011(da)003:145: bcom ldan 'das kyi sprul pa ste //
NK011(da)003:146: yang sprul grangs med phyogs bcur 'phro //
NK011(da)003:148: lho phyogs gshin rje zhabs kyis gnon //
NK011(da)003:149: nub phyogs klu yi gdon rnams gzir //
NK011(da)003:150: byang phyogs gnod sbyin brlag par mdzad //
NK011(da)003:151: shar lho me lha zil gyis gnon //
NK011(da)003:152: lho nub srin po gdan du bting //
NK011(da)003:153: nub byang rlung lha 'ching mdzad cing //
NK011(da)003:154: byang shar dbang ldan brlag par mdzad //
NK011(da)003:155: steng gi lha rnams dbang du bsdus //
NK011(da)003:156: 'og gi sa bdag rdul du rlog /
NK011(da)003:157: phyogs mtshams phur bus gtams byas nas //
NK011(da)003:158: steng 'og yang dag byin gyis rlobs //
NK011(da)003:159: bgegs kyi sbyor ba rgyun chod cig /
NK011(da)003:160: badz+ra kro d+ha rak+sha rak+sha h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:161: yang rang gi thugs ka nas mtshon cha sna tshogs
NK011(da)003:162: pa 'phros srid pa gsum gyi bgegs rnams bcom ste
NK011(da)003:163: tshur 'dus pa las khro bo rnams kyi phyi rol
NK011(da)003:164: du mtshon cha'i gur khang gis gtams par bsam la
NK011(da)003:166: nga yi dkyil 'khor brtan bya'i phyir //
NK011(da)003:167: khro rgyal byin rlabs las byung ba'i //
NK011(da)003:168: rdo rje 'khor lo phur bu dang //
NK011(da)003:169: tho ba ral gri la sogs pa'i //
NK011(da)003:170: mtshon cha rnam pa sna tshogs kyis //
NK011(da)003:171: dkyil 'khor rim pa tshul bzhin bsrung //
NK011(da)003:172: nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
NK011(da)003:173: nga yi bka' las 'da' ma byed //
NK011(da)003:174: badz+ra yu d+ha rak+na rak+sha h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:176: bdud dpung nges par bsreg byed pa'i //
NK011(da)003:177: sa dang nam mkha' yongs gang ba //
NK011(da)003:178: 'bar ba me yi phur por gyur //
NK011(da)003:179: badz+ra dz+wa la ram rak+sha rak+sha h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:180: 'jigs byed 'bar ba nga yi dkyil 'khor du //
NK011(da)003:181: 'dod chags 'joms pa'i me ni dmar nag 'bar //
NK011(da)003:182: zhe sdang 'joms pa'i me ni dkar nag 'bar //
NK011(da)003:183: gti mug 'joms pa'i me ni mthing nag 'bar //
NK011(da)003:184: nga rgyal 'joms pa'i me ni ser nag 'bar //
NK011(da)003:185: phrag dog 'joms pa'i me ni ljang nag 'bar //
NK011(da)003:186: dbang drag gdug rtsub me ni smug nag 'bar //
NK011(da)003:187: 'bar ba me yi mtshams las bgegs ma 'da' //
NK011(da)003:188: badz+ra ag+ne ye dz+wa la ram rak+sha rak+sha h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:189: ces pas de'i phyi rol du me dpung gi gur du bsam /
NK011(da)003:191: mtshams bcad nang 'di tshun chad du //
NK011(da)003:192: su yang 'da' bar ma byed cig /
NK011(da)003:193: gal te 'das par gyur pa na //
NK011(da)003:194: tho ba lcags kyus 'khril ba yis //
NK011(da)003:195: snying nas drangs te brdung bar bya //
NK011(da)003:196: badz+ra ang+ku sha ya dzahbadz+ra mung+ga ra a ko ta ya a ko ta ya h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:197: gsum pa tshogs bsags pa ni /
NK011(da)003:198: rang gi thugs ka'i h+aum las 'od zer 'phros pas
NK011(da)003:199: bla ma yi dam sangs rgyas byang sems mkha' 'gro
NK011(da)003:200: chos skyong thams cad rang bzhin gyi gnas nas badz+ra
NK011(da)003:201: sa m+aa dzah rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal
NK011(da)003:202: // dus gsum bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)003:203: mchog gsum bsten pa'i zhing gyur la //
NK011(da)003:204: gnyis med yid kyis skyabs su mchi //
NK011(da)003:205: dngos 'byor yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK011(da)003:206: dag pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK011(da)003:207: dngos grub chu bo gcod pa'i bgegs //
NK011(da)003:208: nyes byas ma lus bshags par bgyi //
NK011(da)003:209: phyogs bcu 'khor gsum dag pa'i chos //
NK011(da)003:210: ma chags spyod la rjes yi rang //
NK011(da)003:211: dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dri ma med //
NK011(da)003:212: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed de //
NK011(da)003:213: bde gshegs byang chub sems dpa' la //
NK011(da)003:214: dag pa gsum gyi lus 'bul lo //
NK011(da)003:215: tshe rabs bgrangs pa'i las rnams kun //
NK011(da)003:216: bsdus te byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK011(da)003:218: bzhi pa dam bca' ba ni /
NK011(da)003:219: rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i rgya bcings te lhag pa'i bsam pa brtan pos //
NK011(da)003:220: rnal 'byor dbang po ye shes mthar phyin pa //
NK011(da)003:221: 'gro la phan mdzad thugs rjes dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK011(da)003:222: srid pa gsum gyi gnyen gyur gcig pu pa //
NK011(da)003:223: lha yi lha khyod bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK011(da)003:224: bde bar gshegs pa'i sprul pa rgya mtsho dang //
NK011(da)003:225: rnal 'byor dbang phyug grub pa'i tshogs chen po //
NK011(da)003:226: lha dang lha min sngags 'chang dam tshig can //
NK011(da)003:227: kun nas 'dus pa rnams kyang dgongs su gsol //
NK011(da)003:228: bdag ni rgyal srid mtho ris longs spyod dang //
NK011(da)003:229: 'dod pa'i yon tan bdag bsgrub ma lags te //
NK011(da)003:230: 'gro la snying brtse kho nas don brtson pa //
NK011(da)003:231: 'di la kun mkhyen khyod ni dpang du gsol //
NK011(da)003:232: mgon po ye shes sgrib pa mi mnga' bas //
NK011(da)003:233: bdag gi lhag pa'i bsam pa khyed kyis mkhyen //
NK011(da)003:234: 'phags mchog spyan sngar ji ltar dam bcas pa //
NK011(da)003:235: sun par mi bgyi mgon khyod bslu ma lags //
NK011(da)003:236: snying nas bdag ni khe dang grags la sogs //
NK011(da)003:237: g.yo dang zang zing sems ni gtan spangs nas //
NK011(da)003:238: gzhan don sgrub pa gcig pu'i sems bzhag ste //
NK011(da)003:239: rnal 'byor spyod pa chen po bdag gis spyad //
NK011(da)003:240: kun tu bzang po bla na med pa yi //
NK011(da)003:241: byang chub mchog tu bdag gis sems bskyed de //
NK011(da)003:242: don dam dang ni kun rdzob byang chub sems //
NK011(da)003:243: deng nas tshul bzhin yongs su bzung bar bgyi //
NK011(da)003:244: srog chags thams cad gal te bdud gyur nas //
NK011(da)003:245: dum bu stong du bdag gi lus gtubs kyang //
NK011(da)003:246: byang chub sems mchog shes rab snying rje dang //
NK011(da)003:247: yi dam rgyal ba khyed ni yongs mi spong //
NK011(da)003:248: rdo rje'i dam tshig chen po rnams dang ni //
NK011(da)003:249: rdo rje slob dpon rdo rje mched lcam dang //
NK011(da)003:250: gzhan yang theg pa mchog la zhugs pa rnams //
NK011(da)003:251: srog gi phyir yang mi gtong ci nus bsrung //
NK011(da)003:252: 'khor ba bdag med sgyu ma'i rang bzhin la //
NK011(da)003:253: bdag ni 'jigs pa ci yang ma mchis te //
NK011(da)003:254: ma rig skye bo rnams kyi don slad du //
NK011(da)003:255: phyi mthar thug gi bar du gnas par spro //
NK011(da)003:256: gzhan don 'khor ba rnams su spyod pa na //
NK011(da)003:257: byang chub spyod pa rlabs chen bdag gis spyad //
NK011(da)003:258: 'gro drug sems can rnams la phan gdags phyir //
NK011(da)003:259: rang dbang du ni skye ba blang bar bgyi //
NK011(da)003:260: bdag ni yongs su bzung ba'i 'jig rten nam //
NK011(da)003:261: mya ngan 'das la spro ba ma mchis te //
NK011(da)003:262: gang dang gang du sdug bsngal gnas rnams su //
NK011(da)003:263: bskal pa rgya mtshor gnas shing phan par bgyi //
NK011(da)003:264: srid par yun ring dus su brtson pa ni //
NK011(da)003:265: byang chub sems dpa'i yi dam lags pas na //
NK011(da)003:266: ji srid ngan song stongs par ma gyur pa //
NK011(da)003:267: de srid bdag gis skyo ba'i sems mi bskyed //
NK011(da)003:268: shes rab thabs kyis 'gro ba'i don bgyid pa //
NK011(da)003:269: snying rje'i longs spyod de las ma mchis pas //
NK011(da)003:270: sems dmyal yi dwags gshin rje'i 'jig rten yang //
NK011(da)003:271: lha yi dga' tshal lta bur blta bar bgyi //
NK011(da)003:272: 'gro la thugs brtses dpal gyi mgur nas gsungs //
NK011(da)003:273: rnal 'byor dam chos bdud rtsi mchog rnams ni //
NK011(da)003:274: bdag gis 'jig rten thug pa ma mchis par //
NK011(da)003:275: ci ltar mtshams pa bzhin du rgyas par bgyi //
NK011(da)003:276: srid par las dang rkyen gyis dbang gyur te //
NK011(da)003:277: gang dang gang du dam chos 'jig pa der //
NK011(da)003:278: me tshogs spu gri'i so yang brgal nas ni //
NK011(da)003:279: phyi mthar thug gi bar du dam chos gzung //
NK011(da)003:280: bla med byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed de //
NK011(da)003:281: sgrub pa mchog la zhugs pa'i skye bo la //
NK011(da)003:282: tshe rabs rnams su mthu rtsal ci mchis kyis //
NK011(da)003:283: skyes chen rnams kyi dgongs pa rtag tu bskang //
NK011(da)003:284: dam pa'i chos dang sgrub pa'i gegs gyur pa //
NK011(da)003:285: mi dang mi min gdug pa gang yang rung //
NK011(da)003:286: bdag gis zhi dang khro bo'i phrin las kyis //
NK011(da)003:287: yongs su zhi zhing rnam par gzhom par bgyi //
NK011(da)003:288: rnal 'byor mchog gi theg chen bla med dang //
NK011(da)003:289: rdo rje rgyal po khyod la brten nas ni //
NK011(da)003:290: sangs rgyas zhing sbyang 'gro la sman slad du //
NK011(da)003:291: byang chub snying po bdag gis rtogs par bgyi //
NK011(da)003:292: bdag ni 'phags mchog phyag rgyar mngon sprul te //
NK011(da)003:293: gal te skabs med 'chi ba'i dus byung tshe //
NK011(da)003:294: gsang sngags mgon po ye shes dkyil 'khor can //
NK011(da)003:295: khyed kyi zhabs kyi drung du mchi bar bgyi //
NK011(da)003:296: srid gsum sdug bsngal ci 'dra khyed kyis mkhyen //
NK011(da)003:297: dmyal sogs me dpung zhi bar bgyid la sogs //
NK011(da)003:298: sems can don la myur du bdag mchi na //
NK011(da)003:299: dam pa rnams kyi nus mthu stsal du gsol //
NK011(da)003:300: zhes sgyu 'phrul du 'byung ba ltar bya /
NK011(da)003:301: dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes tshogs zhing rnams rang la bstim /
NK011(da)003:302: lnga pa byin dbab pa ni /
NK011(da)003:304: gdal ba chen po chos dbyings pho brang nas //
NK011(da)003:305: rdo rje 'dzin rgyal sangs rgyas 'dus pa'i rje //
NK011(da)003:306: byin rlabs 'dod rgu'i char chen 'bebs mdzad pa //
NK011(da)003:307: phur pa grub pa'i rig 'dzin brgyud par bcas //
NK011(da)003:308: rdo rje gzhon nu'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs kyis //
NK011(da)003:309: sku gsung thugs dang yon tan phrin las kyi //
NK011(da)003:310: mthu dbang byin rlabs dngos grub stsol ba'i phyir //
NK011(da)003:311: dbyings nas 'dir gshegs dkyil 'khor byin phob cig /
NK011(da)003:312: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sa pa ri w+aa ra badz+ra a be sha ya a a a /
NK011(da)003:313: drug pa mchod pa byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK011(da)003:316: rang nyid lha yi thugs ka nas //
NK011(da)003:318: yam 'phros rlung byung bag chags gtor //
NK011(da)003:322: h+aum sdon 'phros te rnam rtog sbyangs //
NK011(da)003:325: h+r+aihyiga kha dog lnga spros zhu //
NK011(da)003:326: lha rnams dgyes pa'i rdzas su gyur //
NK011(da)003:328: so sor brlabs pa la lnga las /
NK011(da)003:330: +aah thod pa snang srid kun khyab gzhal yas su //
NK011(da)003:331: rigs lnga yab yum sbyor ba'i byang sems 'khyil //
NK011(da)003:333: bdud rtsi bkug bstim lha rnams bdud rtsir zhu //
NK011(da)003:334: de las chu bur tshul du rta mgrin dbang //
NK011(da)003:335: yum bzhir bcas pa dag tu gyur pa yang //
NK011(da)003:336: zhu bas kha dog dri dang ro ldan zhing //
NK011(da)003:337: nus mthu phun tshogs bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho che //
NK011(da)003:338: chos dbyings nam mkha'i khams kun gang bar gyur //
NK011(da)003:339: +aah h+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h+aum h+r+aih th+aa /
NK011(da)003:343: b+han+d+ha stong gsum khyab pa'i snod nang du //
NK011(da)003:344: nyon mongs 'gro ba bsgral ba'i rak+ta dang //
NK011(da)003:345: rten 'brel bcu gnyis m+au la rak+ta dang //
NK011(da)003:346: mkha' dbyings dag pa pad+ma rak+ta dang //
NK011(da)003:347: dgra bgegs bsgral ba'i khrag chen rgya mtshor bskyil //
NK011(da)003:348: ra las byung ba'i lha mo rak+ta mo //
NK011(da)003:349: 'bru gsum sbyor bas zhu nas bdud rtsir gyur //
NK011(da)003:350: +aahh+aum ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa la man+da la h+aum h+r+aihth+aa /
NK011(da)003:354: snang ba snod kyi 'jig rten ka p+aa lar //
NK011(da)003:355: sha lnga bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin ri ltar spungs //
NK011(da)003:356: yi ge gsum gyi 'phro 'dus bdud rtsi'i mtsho //
NK011(da)003:357: chos dbyings nam mkha'i mtha' klas gang bar gyur //
NK011(da)003:358: +aahh+aum ma h+aa ba lim ta te dz+wa ba lim
NK011(da)003:359: ta ba la ba te guh+ya sa ma ye s+w+aa
NK011(da)003:362: mchod yon zhabs bsil bdud rtsi'i rgya mtshor bskyil //
NK011(da)003:363: lha rdzas me tog sa dang bar snang khyab //
NK011(da)003:364: spos kyi dud sprin gnam sa bar kun 'khrigs //
NK011(da)003:365: mar me'i phreng ba stong gsum 'od du 'bar //
NK011(da)003:366: spos chu'i rdzing bu snang srid kun tu bskyil //
NK011(da)003:367: zhal zas bdud rtsi'i bcud kyis stong khams bkang //
NK011(da)003:368: lha mi'i rol mo sgra snyan srid gsum 'khrol //
NK011(da)003:369: kun bzang mchod pa'i sprin gyi phung por gyur //
NK011(da)003:377: shap+da p+au dza hoh nang mchod ni /
NK011(da)003:378: khams gsum rnam dag dur khrod gnas mchog tu //
NK011(da)003:379: dbang po lnga yi me tog ri ltar spungs //
NK011(da)003:380: gsur chen dud pa'i sprin phung kun tu 'khrigs //
NK011(da)003:381: zhun chen mar me dus mtha'i me ltar 'bar //
NK011(da)003:382: mchog chen zhag gi byug pa mtsho ru 'khyil //
NK011(da)003:383: sha chen bdud rtsi'i zhal zas 'jig rten gang //
NK011(da)003:384: srid gsum khyab pa'i keng rus brag ltar 'tsher //
NK011(da)003:385: go ro tsa na nam mkha'i rgya khyon gang //
NK011(da)003:386: rkang gling thod rnga'i sgra dbyangs stong gsum sgrog /
NK011(da)003:387: dpag yas nang gi mchod pa bla na med //
NK011(da)003:388: rol pa'i ye shes rdzas su byin gyis brlab //
NK011(da)003:389: ma h+aa rak+ta kem ni ri ti ma h+aa pany+tsa
NK011(da)003:390: p+au dza hoh sgrol mchod kyi phyir ling+ga la dgra
NK011(da)003:391: bgegs dgug gzhug bya ste mchod pa byin gyis rlob
NK011(da)003:392: pa'i rim pa'o // gnyis pa dngos gzhi la /
NK011(da)003:393: ting 'dzin rnam gsum rten brten pa //
NK011(da)003:394: spyan drangs phyag bya gnyis med bstim //
NK011(da)003:395: dbang bskur mchod bstod dzapa bsnyen bya //
NK011(da)003:397: dang po ting 'dzin gsum gyis khog dbub pa ni /
NK011(da)003:399: chos rnams stong zhing bdag med pa //
NK011(da)003:400: nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang nyid las //
NK011(da)003:401: bde chen spros med thig le che //
NK011(da)003:402: ma rtogs rang la rang 'khrul pa'i //
NK011(da)003:403: 'gro drug sems can snying re rje //
NK011(da)003:404: stong nyid snying rje'i ngang can des //
NK011(da)003:405: 'gro don rdzogs par bya ba'i phyir //
NK011(da)003:406: rgyu yi rig pa h+aum du shar //
NK011(da)003:408: gnyis pa rten bskyed pa la gsum las /
NK011(da)003:409: dang po gzhi dbang chen gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK011(da)003:411: stong pa chen po'i ngang du sbyangs //
NK011(da)003:412: e yam ram kham sum kem b+h+r+aum /
NK011(da)003:415: pho brang gzhal yas khang gi gnas //
NK011(da)003:416: nam mkha' sngo skya gru gsum par //
NK011(da)003:417: rlung nag rdo rje rgya gram gtams //
NK011(da)003:418: thams cad 'degs pa'i shugs dang ldan //
NK011(da)003:420: khrag gi rgya mtsho rba rlabs 'khrug /
NK011(da)003:421: zhing chen smug pa'i sa gzhi brdal //
NK011(da)003:422: keng rus chen po'i ri rab la //
NK011(da)003:423: rdo rje brag chen sra ba'i steng //
NK011(da)003:424: gnyis pa rten gzhal yas khang sgom pa ni /
NK011(da)003:425: dur khrod chen po rab 'jigs pa'i //
NK011(da)003:426: dbus su b+h+r+aum las gzhal yas khang //
NK011(da)003:427: phyogs bcur rgya yongs ma chad pa //
NK011(da)003:428: phyi dang nang med kun tu gsal //
NK011(da)003:429: rtsig pa pha gu d+r+wa phyed dang //
NK011(da)003:430: shar bu dang ni mda' yab mdzes //
NK011(da)003:431: stegs gu 'dod yon lha mos gang //
NK011(da)003:432: gru chad bzhi dang ldan pa ste //
NK011(da)003:433: gru bzhi sgo bzhi rta babs mdzes //
NK011(da)003:434: 'bar ba'i bar khyams gnyis dang ldan //
NK011(da)003:435: thod sbrul sna tshogs nyi zlas brjid //
NK011(da)003:436: rgyan rnams kun gyis legs par brgyan //
NK011(da)003:438: phyi nang gnyis su mi dmigs kyang //
NK011(da)003:439: 'gags med ye shes rang snang la //
NK011(da)003:440: nang ni dur khrod gzhal yas khang //
NK011(da)003:441: thod pa skam rlon rtsig pa la //
NK011(da)003:442: kun kyang mig nas me 'bar zhing //
NK011(da)003:443: sna nas dud pa'i sprin phung 'thul //
NK011(da)003:444: kha nas khrag gi zham chu 'bab //
NK011(da)003:445: bar mtshams sha chen 'jim zhal byas //
NK011(da)003:446: sa bdag pho mo'i ka gdan la //
NK011(da)003:447: mchog chen brgyad kyi ka ba byas //
NK011(da)003:448: nyi zla 'bar ba'i ka gzhu la //
NK011(da)003:449: tshangs pa'i gdung bzhi mig mang bris //
NK011(da)003:450: zhing chen zhing chung gral phyam byas //
NK011(da)003:451: zhing lpags thog dang bla bres la //
NK011(da)003:452: rgyu rlon lda ldi don snying 'phyang //
NK011(da)003:453: keng rus thod tshal d+r+wa bas brgyan //
NK011(da)003:454: sgo bzhi sbrul nag re bzhi la //
NK011(da)003:455: nam mkha' lding dang rus sbal gyi //
NK011(da)003:456: ya them ma them rab tu brjid //
NK011(da)003:457: chu srin gdug pa'i lcib khung du //
NK011(da)003:458: zhing gi lpags pas sgo glegs byas //
NK011(da)003:459: zhing chen rgyal mtshan phyogs bzhir sgreng //
NK011(da)003:460: g.yang bzhi rlon pa'i ba dan phyar //
NK011(da)003:461: rgyu ma'i dar dpyang phyogs bcur g.yo //
NK011(da)003:462: tsit+ta rlon pa'i tog gis mtshan //
NK011(da)003:463: ye shes lnga yi me dpung 'bar //
NK011(da)003:464: rdo rje'i 'bar ba'i ra bas bskor //
NK011(da)003:465: 'jigs pa'i dur khrod chen po brgyad //
NK011(da)003:466: gsar dang rnying pa ro yis gang //
NK011(da)003:467: ro langs mang po gar byed cing //
NK011(da)003:468: keng rus me 'bar rgyug cing mchong //
NK011(da)003:469: gsal shing dag gis phug pa'i ro //
NK011(da)003:470: shing la dpyangs dang rengs pa dang //
NK011(da)003:471: rul dang myags dang mes tshig dang //
NK011(da)003:472: mgo dang sha rus lhu dum 'thor //
NK011(da)003:473: dur bya gshog brdab lce spyang 'khrug /
NK011(da)003:474: phyogs skyong zhing skyong lha dang klu //
NK011(da)003:475: 'dre dang sha za srin po dag /
NK011(da)003:476: 'jigs pa'i ca co cher sgrog cing //
NK011(da)003:477: me chu shing dang mchod rten sprin //
NK011(da)003:478: khrag mtsho khol ma dag dang bcas //
NK011(da)003:479: mkha' 'gro ma yis bdag byas shing //
NK011(da)003:480: rab 'jigs kun tu skyi g.ya' ba //
NK011(da)003:481: grub pa'i rnal 'byor rgyu ba'i gnas //
NK011(da)003:482: 'bar ba brgyad kyis bskor ba yi //
NK011(da)003:483: dkyil 'khor chen por lhun gyis grub //
NK011(da)003:484: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he b+hany+dza dz+ny+aa na tsakra man+da la b+h+r+aum /
NK011(da)003:485: de dbus mthing nag gru gsum e //
NK011(da)003:486: zla gam khrag mtsho gsum dang ldan //
NK011(da)003:488: mu khyud thod pa'i ra bar bcas //
NK011(da)003:489: gsum pa gdan bskyed pa ni /
NK011(da)003:491: thugs ka nas khro bo lcags kyu dang tho ba thogs pa mang po 'phros nas /
NK011(da)003:493: phyogs skyong rnams kyi snying ga nas lcags kyus bzung /
NK011(da)003:494: tho bas nyal gyis brdungs nas dbus dang rtsibs bcur bzhag par bsam la /
NK011(da)003:495: dzah bdag nyid dpal gyi thugs ka nas //
NK011(da)003:497: lha chen dregs pa khyo shugs dang //
NK011(da)003:498: phyogs skyong 'byung po gdan du bting //
NK011(da)003:503: u ma de w+ai dzah brah+ma na dzah in+d+ra ye
NK011(da)003:504: dzah ag+ne ye dzah ya ma ye dzah nee r+ai
NK011(da)003:505: t+ya dzah wa ru n+aa ya dzah w+aa ya be
NK011(da)003:506: dzah ku be r+aa ye dzah i sha na ya
NK011(da)003:507: dzah b+h+au mi pa ti dzah m+aa ra dzahzhesa pas
NK011(da)003:508: ma h+aa de wa pho mo dbus su gtso bo'i
NK011(da)003:509: gdan dang / phyogs skyong rnams rtsibs stengs su khro bo rnams kyi gdan bting bar bsam mo //
NK011(da)003:510: gsum pa brten pa lha bskyed pa la gsum ste /
NK011(da)003:513: phur bu rdzas kyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'o //
NK011(da)003:514: dang po bdag rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa la'ang gsum las /
NK011(da)003:515: dang po bskyed pa dngos ni /
NK011(da)003:517: chos nyid stong pa'i rang sgra las //
NK011(da)003:518: rgyu yi ting 'dzin yi ge h+aum //
NK011(da)003:519: rdo rje h+aum gis mtshan par gyur //
NK011(da)003:520: de nyid dbus kyi gdan steng babs //
NK011(da)003:522: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+h+n+aam bam h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:523: snang stong rdo rje chos kyi sku //
NK011(da)003:524: dpal chen khro rgyal gzhon nu ni //
NK011(da)003:525: mthing nag dkar dmar 'jigs pa'i zhal //
NK011(da)003:526: rdo rje rtse dgu rtse lnga dang //
NK011(da)003:527: me dpung dang ni kha t+wam thogs //
NK011(da)003:528: ri rab brjid pa'i phur pa 'dril //
NK011(da)003:529: rab 'jigs srin po khros pa'i gzugs //
NK011(da)003:530: dur khrod 'bar ba'i chas dang ldan //
NK011(da)003:531: rdo rje'i gshog pa nam mkhar gdengs //
NK011(da)003:532: dkar dmar ljang nag sbrul chen gyis //
NK011(da)003:533: dbur brgyan se ral sked bcings dang //
NK011(da)003:534: phyag dang zhabs gnyis rnam par spras //
NK011(da)003:535: dbu la rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas rdzogs //
NK011(da)003:536: zhabs bzhi dor stabs dregs pa bardzisa //
NK011(da)003:537: ye shes bskal pa'i me klong bzhugs //
NK011(da)003:538: gar dgu'i nyams ldan dpa' bo che //
NK011(da)003:539: thugs kar rang 'dra'i sems dpa' ni //
NK011(da)003:540: smug nag 'bar ba tshon gang ba'i //
NK011(da)003:541: thugs kar rdo rje h'u dang ldan //
NK011(da)003:542: mtha' mar k+ai la ya yis bskos //
NK011(da)003:543: thugs na rin chen zur brgyad pa //
NK011(da)003:544: zla gam sgo gcig lta bu'i tshul //
NK011(da)003:545: sgo srung rta mgrin rgyal por gsal //
NK011(da)003:546: bdag gi phung khams skye mched dang //
NK011(da)003:547: skra dang ba spur bcas pa kun //
NK011(da)003:548: rang 'dra'i rdo rje gzhon nu ni //
NK011(da)003:549: k+ai la ya yi sgra sgrog cing //
NK011(da)003:550: go mtshams med par gtams par gyur //
NK011(da)003:551: t+aip+ta tsakra ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK011(da)003:554: gzig sham phyag rgya lnga yis spras //
NK011(da)003:555: thod skam dbu rgyan do shal 'phyang //
NK011(da)003:556: khro bo'i chas rnams rdzogs par gsal //
NK011(da)003:558: snod bcud gzhal yas lha ru gyur //
NK011(da)003:559: gnyis pa spyan drangs shing byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK011(da)003:561: rdo rje gzhon nu'i rig 'dzin rnams //
NK011(da)003:562: srid pa rdo rje sgrub par mdzod //
NK011(da)003:565: slar yang thugs ka'i 'od zer gyis //
NK011(da)003:566: ye shes sems dpa' spyan drangs te //
NK011(da)003:567: srid pa rdo rje phur pa'i lha //
NK011(da)003:568: ye shes khro bo'i 'grub par mdzod //
NK011(da)003:569: sarba ta th+aa ga ta badz+ra sam ya dzah dzahh+aum
NK011(da)003:570: bam hoh zhes pas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK011(da)003:571: rdo rje phur pa'i lha tshogs kyi rnam par byon
NK011(da)003:572: nas / bcud kyi sems can thams cad lha dang
NK011(da)003:573: lha mor gsal bde dag la bstims pas snod bcud
NK011(da)003:576: bdag gi gnas gsum 'bru gsum las //
NK011(da)003:578: sku gsung thugs kyi lha rnams kun //
NK011(da)003:579: ma lus spyan drangs thim pa las //
NK011(da)003:580: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rjer gyur //
NK011(da)003:582: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes sku //
NK011(da)003:583: ngang nyid rdo rje chos dbyings las //
NK011(da)003:584: 'bar ba'i khro bo mi bzad pa //
NK011(da)003:585: sku yi dbyig tu bdag bskyed cig /
NK011(da)003:586: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK011(da)003:587: de bzhin du w+aa ka dang tsit+ta zhes sbyar te brjod /
NK011(da)003:590: yab kyi gsang gnas mi dmigs pad zla nyir //
NK011(da)003:591: rdo rje h+aum dang rwa lnga 'bru lngas mtshan //
NK011(da)003:592: yum gyi mkha' gsang nyi zla pad+ma'i steng //
NK011(da)003:593: gru gsum mthing nag e yis mtshan par gyur //
NK011(da)003:598: rigs lnga mkha' la spyan drangs te //
NK011(da)003:599: ma h+aa sarba p+au dza hoh mchod pa chen pos dgyes byas nas /
NK011(da)003:601: thabs kyi spyod pas 'gro don du //
NK011(da)003:602: byams dang snying rjes gang 'dul ba //
NK011(da)003:603: sangs rgyas phrin las rdzogs mdzad nas //
NK011(da)003:604: dbang dang byin rlabs 'dir stsol cig /
NK011(da)003:605: badz+ri b+ha wa a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK011(da)003:606: ye shes chu yis dbang bskur bas //
NK011(da)003:607: dri ma sbyangs te lud pa las //
NK011(da)003:608: rigs lnga yab yum he ru kas //
NK011(da)003:609: dbu la rab tu brgyan par gyur //
NK011(da)003:610: h+aum t+r+aam h+r+aih+aah m+aum l+aam m+aam p+aam t+aam /
NK011(da)003:611: sh+ri he ru ka krod+hi shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK011(da)003:612: gnyis pa phyogs bcu khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa la gnyis te /
NK011(da)003:613: khro bcu yab yum phyag brnyan dang bcas par bskyed pa dang /
NK011(da)003:614: zhar byung sgo skyong dam can dang bcas par bskyed pa'o //
NK011(da)003:616: yum gyis sa ma ya s+t+wam zhes bskul bas /
NK011(da)003:617: yab kyis sa ma ya hohzhesa dang /
NK011(da)003:619: yab yum gnyis med sbyor ba'i byin rlabs las //
NK011(da)003:620: byang sems sprin 'phros 'gro rnams bde la bkod //
NK011(da)003:621: tshur 'dus gdan thog bcu ru thig le bcu //
NK011(da)003:622: thugs ka'i h+aum las h+aum yig sbrel ma bcu //
NK011(da)003:623: 'phros nas thig le bcu yi nang du zhugs //
NK011(da)003:624: khro bcu yab yum sprul par bcas rnams gsal //
NK011(da)003:636: zung bcu gdan so so'i steng du chad de yongs su gyur pa las /
NK011(da)003:638: yab yum gnyis med sbyor ba las //
NK011(da)003:639: byung ba'i phyogs bcu'i khro bo ni //
NK011(da)003:640: thams cad zhal gsum phyag drug pa //
NK011(da)003:641: spyan dgu zhabs kyang bzhi pa ste //
NK011(da)003:642: dur khrod 'bar ba'i chas kyis brgyan //
NK011(da)003:643: rtsa ba'i phyag gnyis dag gis ni //
NK011(da)003:644: rdo rje dung dmar dkrug cing gsol //
NK011(da)003:645: tha gnyis ri rab phur bu sgril //
NK011(da)003:647: badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum k+aa ra h+aum gardza gardza h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:648: steng phyogs khro bo h+aum mdzad sngo //
NK011(da)003:649: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar sgra 'byin yum //
NK011(da)003:650: bar pa'i phyag gnyis mda' gzhu 'gengs //
NK011(da)003:651: sprul pa phag dang rtsang pa'i mgo //
NK011(da)003:652: badz+ra kro d+ha bi dza ya h+aum ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:653: shar phyogs khro bo rnam par rgyal //
NK011(da)003:654: dkar dmar sngo zhing snyems ma yum //
NK011(da)003:656: sprul pa stag dang bya rgod mgo //
NK011(da)003:657: badz+ra kro d+ha ni la dan+da h+aum da ha da ha h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:658: shar lho khro bo dbyug sngon sngo //
NK011(da)003:659: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar sder mo yum //
NK011(da)003:660: bar pa dbyug tho me dbal bsnams //
NK011(da)003:661: sprul pa g.yag dang bya rog mgo //
NK011(da)003:662: badz+ra kro d+ha ya m+aan+ta ka h+aum pa tsa pa tsa h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:663: lho ru gshin rje gshed po mthing //
NK011(da)003:664: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dur khrod yum //
NK011(da)003:665: bar pa dgra s+t+wa dbyug tho 'dzin //
NK011(da)003:666: sprul pa sha ba 'ug pa'i mgo //
NK011(da)003:667: badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya +aa tsa la h+aum b+han+d+ha b+han+d+ha h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:668: lho nub khro bo mi g.yo smug /
NK011(da)003:669: g.yas dkar g.yon ljang gtun khung yum //
NK011(da)003:670: bar pa ral gri zhags pa 'dzin //
NK011(da)003:671: sprul pa gzig dang khwa ta'i mgo //
NK011(da)003:672: badz+ra kro d+ha h+ya g+r+ai ba h+aum hu lu hu lu h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:673: nub tu khro bo rta mgrin dmar //
NK011(da)003:674: g.yas dkar g.yon mthing gtum mo yum //
NK011(da)003:675: bar pa ral gri sbrul zhags 'dzin //
NK011(da)003:676: sprul pa byi la pu shud mgo //
NK011(da)003:677: badz+ra kro d+ha a pa ra dzi ta h+aum tish+tha tish+tha h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:678: nub byang khro bo 'dod rgyal dmar //
NK011(da)003:679: g.yas dkar g.yon ljang mda' snyems yum //
NK011(da)003:680: bar pa dbyug tho rnga yab 'dzin //
NK011(da)003:681: sprul pa spyang ki khra yi mgo //
NK011(da)003:682: badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da li h+aum ts+tshin+d+ha ts+tshin+d+ha h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:683: byang du bdud rtsi 'khyil ba ljang //
NK011(da)003:684: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar rlung 'byin yul //
NK011(da)003:685: bar pa rgya gram dbyug tho 'dzin //
NK011(da)003:686: sprul pa seng ge pha wam mgo //
NK011(da)003:687: badz+ra kro d+ha tree lokya bi dza ya h+aum b+hin+d+ha b+hin+d+ha h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:688: byang shar khro bo bgegs 'dul ser //
NK011(da)003:689: g.yas mthing g.yon ljang gsod byed yum //
NK011(da)003:690: bar pa rdo rje tri shul 'dzin //
NK011(da)003:691: sprul pa dred dang sre mong mgo //
NK011(da)003:692: badz+ra kro d+ha ma h+aa ba la h+aum s+pho ta s+pho ta h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:693: 'og phyogs stobs chen dud kha 'i mdog /
NK011(da)003:694: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar bskyod byed yum //
NK011(da)003:695: bar pa tho ba gtun shing 'dzin //
NK011(da)003:696: sprul pa dom dang byi ba'i mgo //
NK011(da)003:697: yab rnams cha lugs gtso dang mtshungs //
NK011(da)003:698: rang rang yum rnams sku mdog dang //
NK011(da)003:699: cha lugs gtso mo dag dang mthun //
NK011(da)003:700: phyag mtshan dril bu dung dmar 'dzin //
NK011(da)003:701: sprul pa lcam dral sku mdog ni //
NK011(da)003:702: g.yas g.yon zhal gyi kha dog 'dzin //
NK011(da)003:703: phyag mtshan sna tshogs phur bu thogs //
NK011(da)003:704: rngams brjid 'bar ba'i sku ru bskyed //
NK011(da)003:706: gtso ba'i thugs ka nas dzahh+aum bam hohbazhi spros te sgo bzhir 'khod pa ni /
NK011(da)003:707: shar gyi sgo ba pu shud mgo //
NK011(da)003:708: mthing nag g.yas pa lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK011(da)003:709: lho yi sgo ba skya ka'i mgo //
NK011(da)003:710: ser mo g.yas pa zhags pa 'dzin //
NK011(da)003:711: nub kyi sgo ba srin bya'i mgo //
NK011(da)003:712: dmar nag g.yas pa lcags sgrog 'dzin //
NK011(da)003:713: byang gi sgo ba khra yi mgo //
NK011(da)003:714: ljang nag g.yas pa dril bu 'dzin //
NK011(da)003:715: kun kyang g.yon pa phur bu thogs //
NK011(da)003:716: rgyan dang cha lugs rdzogs par bskyed //
NK011(da)003:717: de nas dam can 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK011(da)003:718: khrag khyams zhing skam gdan stengs su //
NK011(da)003:719: dbang phyug chen po'i nyi shu brgyad //
NK011(da)003:720: smug nag ser nag dmar nag dang //
NK011(da)003:721: ljang nag bdun bzhi phyogs bzhir bskyed //
NK011(da)003:722: khrag khyams phyi rol lha snam gnyis //
NK011(da)003:723: mi ro rta ros gang ba'i steng //
NK011(da)003:724: nang ngos phur srung bcu gnyis dang //
NK011(da)003:725: phyi rol ma mo ging gi tshogs //
NK011(da)003:726: shar sgor dung gi skyes bu dang //
NK011(da)003:727: lho sgor lcags kyi skyes bu dang //
NK011(da)003:728: nub sgor bse yi skyes bu dang //
NK011(da)003:729: byang sgor ta ki nag po bskyed //
NK011(da)003:730: gzhan yang bar khyams khor yug la //
NK011(da)003:731: mkha' 'gro chen mo sum cu gnyis //
NK011(da)003:732: ging chen pho mo bco brgyad dang //
NK011(da)003:733: 'bar ba'i pho nya ma mo bdun //
NK011(da)003:734: sring bzhi brtan ma bcu gnyis dang //
NK011(da)003:735: dge bsnyen nyi shu rtsa gcig rnams //
NK011(da)003:737: gsum pa phur pa rdzas kyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK011(da)003:739: bdag gi thugs ka'i 'od zer gyis //
NK011(da)003:741: srid gsum gdug pa bkug nas ni //
NK011(da)003:742: gan rkyal kha sbub bskyel bar gyur //
NK011(da)003:743: ces pas phur gdan e las chos 'byung gi nang
NK011(da)003:744: du n+ri tri las dgra bgegs bskyed de dgug gzhug
NK011(da)003:745: bya / de nas byin gyis brlab pa la bdun te /
NK011(da)003:747: snang zhing srid pa'i chos rnams kun //
NK011(da)003:748: byang chub sems kyi phur pa ste //
NK011(da)003:749: phur pa'i rang bzhin gdod nas dag /
NK011(da)003:750: blo bral chos kyi sku ru gsal //
NK011(da)003:752: skye med 'gags pa med pa'i rang rtsal las //
NK011(da)003:753: h+aum las skyes pa'i drag po'i phur bu ste //
NK011(da)003:754: rgya mdun dang po b+h+r+aum las gzhal yas khang //
NK011(da)003:755: 'bru lnga yongs gyur khrag 'thung rigs lnga la //
NK011(da)003:756: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod sprin rgya mtshos mchod //
NK011(da)003:757: bdag gi las kyi 'bras bu mchis par mdzod //
NK011(da)003:759: ji ltar shel la tshon gyis bsgyur ba ltar //
NK011(da)003:760: longs spyod rdzogs las thugs rje sprul pa'i sku //
NK011(da)003:761: khro rgyal 'dus pa'i sras mchog k+ai la ya //
NK011(da)003:762: sku stod khro bo zhal gcig phyag bzhi pa //
NK011(da)003:763: sku smad rno dbal phur bu 'bar ba'i tshul //
NK011(da)003:764: kham nag ral pa zur gsum stabs su sgreng //
NK011(da)003:765: sbrul chen 'jigs pas thod rlon bcings shing spras //
NK011(da)003:766: spyan gsum sdang mig rab bgrad phyogs bcur gzigs //
NK011(da)003:767: gtum rngams mche gtsigs me dpung klong na bzhugs //
NK011(da)003:768: phyag bzhi g.yas na 'bar ba'i s+t+wa re 'phyar //
NK011(da)003:769: 'og ma rdo rje ri rab gnon stabs 'dzin //
NK011(da)003:770: kha t+w+aam 'khrol bas khams gsum 'jigs par mdzad //
NK011(da)003:771: phur bu 'debs pas ngan song gsum po 'jig /
NK011(da)003:772: khyod kyi nus mthu stobs dang drag rtsal ni //
NK011(da)003:773: khro bo thams cad 'dus pa bas kyang che //
NK011(da)003:774: brtag pa chen po sprul skur byin brlabs pa'i //
NK011(da)003:775: gnas lnga dpa' bo 'bru lngas mtshan par bsam /
NK011(da)003:776: +aahh+aum s+w+aa h+aah zhes sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lngar byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK011(da)003:777: phur bu de yi spyi mgrin rtse mo ru //
NK011(da)003:778: dang h+r+aihdang phata kyis mtshan pa las /
NK011(da)003:780: sku dang gsung dang thugs su byin brlabs gyur //
NK011(da)003:781: ces sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlab pa'o //
NK011(da)003:782: dpal zur phata gsum ngos gsum h+aum gis mtshan //
NK011(da)003:783: thugs rje ye shes rtse mo gcig par brlabs //
NK011(da)003:784: thugs ye shes rtse gcig par byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK011(da)003:785: bdag nyid rtsa ba'i thugs ka'i 'od zer gyis //
NK011(da)003:786: rigs kyi khro bo thams cad spyan drangs te //
NK011(da)003:787: ma h+aa p+au dza hoh h+aum t+r+aam h+r+aih+aah sh+r+ai he
NK011(da)003:788: ru ka bud+d+ha badz+ra rat+na pad+ma karma a b+hi shiny+tsa
NK011(da)003:789: h+aum / de nas rol pa khro bo'i lha tshogs rnams //
NK011(da)003:790: phyogs bcur sprul pa 'phros te tshur 'dus nas //
NK011(da)003:791: h+aum phata 'jigs pa'i gad rgyang cher sgrog cing //
NK011(da)003:792: phur pa la thim dbang dang byin rlabs rdzogs //
NK011(da)003:793: zhes rigs so so'i khro bos dbang bskur zhing byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK011(da)003:795: bdag nyid phyag g.yas ma las nyi steng h+aum //
NK011(da)003:796: g.yon par a las zla steng yi ge a //
NK011(da)003:797: lag sor g.yas la nyi dkyil re re'i steng //
NK011(da)003:798: h+aum t+r+aam h+r+aih +aah rnams kyis mtshan pa //
NK011(da)003:799: g.yon sor lnga la zla dkyil re re'i steng //
NK011(da)003:800: l+aam m+aam m+aum p+aam t+aam rnams kyis mtshan pa //
NK011(da)003:801: de dag yongs gyur rigs lnga yab yum bcu //
NK011(da)003:802: sku mdog cha lugs rgyan rnams rdzogs par gyur //
NK011(da)003:805: badz+ra any+tsa li h+aum gis sor mo bsnol /
NK011(da)003:806: badz+ra b+han+d+ha h+aum gis phyag rgya bsdams /
NK011(da)003:808: de nas phur bu lag tu blangs te changs bar bcug /
NK011(da)003:809: lag pa'i rting pa'i mkhrig ma bsnyal mthe bong gnyis
NK011(da)003:810: dang srin lag dang mathe'u chung gi bar du phur
NK011(da)003:811: bu gzhug / mthe bong cung zad bsgul bas 'dril la /
NK011(da)003:812: badz+ra a be sha ya a a /
NK011(da)003:813: phyogs bcu dus gsum rgyal sras 'khor dang bcas //
NK011(da)003:814: sngon gyi thugs dam sdong grogs rjes dgongs la //
NK011(da)003:815: bu yug 'tshub ltar gshegs nas phur par thim //
NK011(da)003:816: sku gsung thugs kyi bdag nyid chen por bzhugs //
NK011(da)003:817: phur bu bdag nyid chen por byin gyis brlab cing dbang bskur ba'o //
NK011(da)003:818: de nas sor mo rgyab tu bsnol la /
NK011(da)003:819: gong mo gnyis gshib nas bsgreng ba'i bar du phur bu bcug la /
NK011(da)003:821: de nas sor mo pug pug por byas la /
NK011(da)003:822: lag pa'i rting pas phur bu bzung la /
NK011(da)003:824: de nas sor mo rgyab tu bsnol te mthe bong gshib nas phur bu bzung ste /
NK011(da)003:825: ts+tshin+d+ha ts+tshin+d+ha ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:828: bdag nyid che rnams thams cad kyang //
NK011(da)003:829: gnyis med sbyor ba'i gzi byin rnams //
NK011(da)003:830: phur pa la ni zhugs pa yis //
NK011(da)003:831: stong khams gang ba'i me stag 'phros //
NK011(da)003:832: dmigs pa'i las rnams nges 'grub pa'i //
NK011(da)003:833: dbang chen ldan par byin gyis brlabs //
NK011(da)003:834: zhes don dran bzhin pas mdun gyi e steng du bzhugs su gsol /
NK011(da)003:835: de ni bdag nyid chen por yongs su rdzogs par byin gyis brlabs shing dbang bskur ba'o //
NK011(da)003:836: de nas yungs kar brab cing gzi mdangs bskyed pa ni /
NK011(da)003:837: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha tshal pa h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:838: gu gul gyis bdug cing nus pa bskyed pa ni /
NK011(da)003:839: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya d+hu pe ta li ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:840: rak+ta phur rtse la byug pas chags pa bskyed pa ni /
NK011(da)003:841: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa
NK011(da)003:842: la man+da la dgra bgegs m+aa ra ya h+aum phata
NK011(da)003:845: mthing nag gcer bu ral pa can //
NK011(da)003:846: sku stod khro bo chen po la //
NK011(da)003:847: lte ba man chad phur pa'i dbal //
NK011(da)003:849: dbu la rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas rdzogs //
NK011(da)003:850: thugs la rdo rje gzhon nu 'bar //
NK011(da)003:851: ye shes me dpung klong na bzhugs //
NK011(da)003:852: drag por gyur pa'i phur pa ste //
NK011(da)003:853: btab na lha yang brlag 'gyur na //
NK011(da)003:854: gnod byed rnams la smos ci dgos //
NK011(da)003:855: dgra bgegs snying la k+ai la ya //
NK011(da)003:856: rdzas kyi byin gyis brlab cing che ba brjod pa'o //
NK011(da)003:857: de nas ye shes kyi 'od zer gyis dkyil 'khor
NK011(da)003:858: gsum la srog ye shes su dbang bskur zhes pas
NK011(da)003:859: / bdag rtsa ba dang phur pa rdzas la dbang bskur ba sngar song la 'dir /
NK011(da)003:860: khro bcu yab yum khra thabs sgo ma dang bcas
NK011(da)003:861: pa rnams kyi gnas gsum du +aahh+aum dkar dmar mthing
NK011(da)003:862: gsum gyis mtshan par bsam mo //
NK011(da)003:863: bzhi pa rang bzhin ye shes kyi 'khor lo spyan drang ba ni /
NK011(da)003:864: rang gi thugs ka'i h+aum gi 'od zer gyis rang
NK011(da)003:865: bzhin gya gnas nas rdo rje gzhon nu la sangs
NK011(da)003:866: rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs kyis bskor ba
NK011(da)003:867: phur pa'i lha tshogs kyi rnam par spyan drangs par
NK011(da)003:869: phyogs dus dkyil 'khor bdag nyid che //
NK011(da)003:870: mi dmigs thugs kyi dkyil 'khor las //
NK011(da)003:871: dkyil 'khor thams cad spyan drang ngo //
NK011(da)003:872: rang snang dbyer med dkyil 'khor la //
NK011(da)003:873: 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid mnyam sbyor bas //
NK011(da)003:874: phyogs dus kun nas gshegs pa yi //
NK011(da)003:875: snying po'i dkyil 'khor lhun gyis rdzogs //
NK011(da)003:876: srid pa'i phur bu sgrub pa dang //
NK011(da)003:877: dbang dang dngos grub blang ba'i phyir //
NK011(da)003:878: ye shes khro bo gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)003:879: khro bo chen po gshegs nas kyang //
NK011(da)003:880: rtags dang mtshan ma bstan pa dang //
NK011(da)003:881: k+ai la ya yi dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)003:882: badz+ra sa m+aa dzah zhes pas /
NK011(da)003:883: ye shes kyi 'khor lo ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil
NK011(da)003:884: 'khor la mngon du phyogs pa'i mdun gyi nam mkhar
NK011(da)003:885: bzhugs par bsam / lnga pa phyag bya ba ni /
NK011(da)003:887: srid gsum gdug pa 'dul ba dang //
NK011(da)003:888: nga rgyal zhen pa gzhom pa'i phyir //
NK011(da)003:889: rdo rje srin po'i lha tshogs la //
NK011(da)003:890: rtse gcig gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)003:891: a ti pu hoh pra t+aits+tsha hoh zhes phyag bya /
NK011(da)003:893: sh+r+ai he ru ka sa pa ri w+aa ra p+aa
NK011(da)003:894: d+yam pra t+aits+tsha s+w+aa h+aah badz+ra +aa sa na ti
NK011(da)003:895: sh+than+tu / zhes zhabs bsil zhing gdan la bzhugs /
NK011(da)003:896: ma h+aa p+au dza hoh zhes mchod nas /
NK011(da)003:897: dzahh+aum bam hoh sa gnyis su med par bstim /
NK011(da)003:898: bdun pa dbang bskur ba ni /
NK011(da)003:900: bdag nyid sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK011(da)003:901: rje btsun ye nas yin pa'i phyir //
NK011(da)003:902: sku gsung thugs su byin rlob cing //
NK011(da)003:903: ye shes lnga yi dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)003:905: 'khor gyi lha tshogs thams cad la //
NK011(da)003:906: gtso bo yis ni dbu brgyan cing //
NK011(da)003:907: dam can phur srung tshogs rnams la //
NK011(da)003:908: dbang rtags rdo rjes mtshan par gyur //
NK011(da)003:909: brgyad pa mchod pa la brgyad las /
NK011(da)003:912: dag cing dri med mchod yon dam pa dang //
NK011(da)003:913: me tog bdug spos snang gsal byug pa'i mtsho //
NK011(da)003:914: zhal zas sgra snyan la sogs mchod pa'i sprin //
NK011(da)003:915: dngos su 'byor dang yid kyis rnam sprul pa //
NK011(da)003:916: chos dbyings nam mkha'i khams rnams yongs bkang ste //
NK011(da)003:917: zag med bde chen kun bzang mchod pa'i sprin //
NK011(da)003:918: srid pa ji srid 'byung bar byin brlabs te //
NK011(da)003:919: rdo rje phur pa'i dkyil 'khor lha la 'bul //
NK011(da)003:920: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sa pa ri w+aa ra ar+g+ham /
NK011(da)003:926: shap+ta p+au dza me g+ha sa mu dra s+pha ra na sa ma ye h+aum /
NK011(da)003:927: gnyis pa 'dod yon gyi mchod pa ni /
NK011(da)003:929: gzugs kyi lha mo yid 'ong ma //
NK011(da)003:930: dkar mo mdzes ma me long 'dzin //
NK011(da)003:932: spyan gyi mchod pas mnyes gyur cig /
NK011(da)003:933: sgra yi lha mo yid 'ong ma //
NK011(da)003:934: ser mo dbyangs snyan pi wam 'dzin //
NK011(da)003:936: snyan gyi mchod pas mnyes gyur cig /
NK011(da)003:937: dri yi lha mo yid 'ong ma //
NK011(da)003:938: sngon mo mdzes ma spos phor 'dzin //
NK011(da)003:940: shangs kyi mchod pa mnyes gyur cig /
NK011(da)003:941: ro yi lha mo yid 'ong ma //
NK011(da)003:942: dmar mo mdzes ma zhal zas 'dzin //
NK011(da)003:944: ljags kyi mchod pas mnyes gyur cig /
NK011(da)003:945: reg bya'i lha mo yid 'ong ma //
NK011(da)003:948: sku yi mchod pas mnyes gyur cig /
NK011(da)003:949: chos kyi lha mo yid 'ong ma //
NK011(da)003:952: thugs kyi mchod pas mnyes gyur cig /
NK011(da)003:953: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sa pa ri w+aa ra /
NK011(da)003:959: d+harma p+au dza hoh gsum pa phyag rgya gar mchod ni /
NK011(da)003:961: khrag 'thung rgyal po gar la dgyes //
NK011(da)003:962: sku mdog zhal ni rnam par 'gyur //
NK011(da)003:963: sku yi gar stabs glog 'gyu ba'i //
NK011(da)003:964: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa 'bul //
NK011(da)003:965: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya ma h+aa mu dra p+au dza hoh zhes phyag rgya bcing ngo //
NK011(da)003:968: rdo rje phur bu'i lha tshogs la //
NK011(da)003:970: 'khril ba'i mchod chen mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK011(da)003:971: bdag nyid mnyes pas mnyes par mdzod //
NK011(da)003:972: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK011(da)003:974: a nu r+aa ga ya mye /
NK011(da)003:975: dzahh+aum bam hoh bo d+hi tsit+ta s+pha ra na phata /
NK011(da)003:978: rang byung gdong nas dag pa ste //
NK011(da)003:979: rtsa brgyad stong las sbyar ba'i sman //
NK011(da)003:980: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga yi dngos //
NK011(da)003:981: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas //
NK011(da)003:982: rgyud drug sems can kun sgrol phyir //
NK011(da)003:983: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK011(da)003:984: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba thams cad dang //
NK011(da)003:985: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs chen por //
NK011(da)003:986: bdag cag dad pas 'bul lags na //
NK011(da)003:987: bzhes nas 'phrul gyi dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)003:988: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)003:989: rgyal ba kun dngos rtsa brgyud bla ma dang //
NK011(da)003:990: dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu yab yum la //
NK011(da)003:991: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK011(da)003:992: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)003:993: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)003:994: 'jigs byed chen po khro rgyal yab yum bcu //
NK011(da)003:995: za gsod khra thabs nyi shu sgo srung bzhir //
NK011(da)003:996: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK011(da)003:997: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)003:998: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)003:999: las bzhi'i phrin las mdzad pa'i pho brang du //
NK011(da)003:1000: sras mchog phur pa'i lha tshogs thams cad la //
NK011(da)003:1001: rnam dag thugs rjes ma h+aa phyi nang mkha' 'gro 'khor bcas thams cad dang //
NK011(da)003:1002: dam can bcu gnyis ging dang bcas pa la //
NK011(da)003:1003: rnam dag thugs rjes ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)003:1004: dge bsnyen nyer gcig brtan ma bcu gnyis sogs //
NK011(da)003:1005: phur pa'i srung mar zhal bzhes thams cad la //
NK011(da)003:1006: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK011(da)003:1007: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)003:1008: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)003:1009: sdom la gnas shing rig 'dzin sgrub pa po //
NK011(da)003:1010: lha dang lha min phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor la //
NK011(da)003:1011: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK011(da)003:1012: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)003:1013: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)003:1014: zhes bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho las mtheb srin nyi zla
NK011(da)003:1015: gwa 'us bcus te phul bas lha thams cad bde
NK011(da)003:1016: ba chen po'i ros mnyes par bsam mo //
NK011(da)003:1017: de ltar mchod yul rnams mnyes pas sku gsung thugs
NK011(da)003:1018: kyi dngos grub +aahh+aum gi rnam par bdud rtsi'i nang
NK011(da)003:1019: du bab pa las dngos grub blangs te /
NK011(da)003:1021: lce yi dam tshig rdo rje la //
NK011(da)003:1022: rdo rje can gyi h+aum bsgoms te //
NK011(da)003:1023: bdud rtsi lnga dang sbyar ba'i sman //
NK011(da)003:1024: zos na sku gsung thugs thob 'gyur //
NK011(da)003:1026: w+aa ka sid+d+hi +aah tsit+ta sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK011(da)003:1027: zhes 'bru gsum mtheb srin gyis blangs nas lcer bzhag pas /
NK011(da)003:1028: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob par bsam mo //
NK011(da)003:1029: drug par rak+ta'i mchod pa ni /
NK011(da)003:1031: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK011(da)003:1032: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NK011(da)003:1033: dpal chen khrag 'thung spyan drangs te //
NK011(da)003:1034: dur khrod mchog gi gnas 'di ru //
NK011(da)003:1035: zhing chen gsar rnying ti rar bcas //
NK011(da)003:1036: dmar gyi ar+g+ham rgya mtshor bskyil //
NK011(da)003:1038: ma lus gshegs nas bsnams su gsol //
NK011(da)003:1039: sarba dush+tam ru dra m+aa ra ya kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)003:1041: nga ni za byed chen po ste //
NK011(da)003:1042: khams gsum ma lus bsgral ba dang //
NK011(da)003:1043: gdul dka' ma lus 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK011(da)003:1044: sha rus la sogs za bar bya //
NK011(da)003:1046: nga ni khrag 'thung chen po ste //
NK011(da)003:1047: 'khor ba'i d+r+wa bar chags pa yis //
NK011(da)003:1048: dmar chen khrag gi ar+g+ham la /
NK011(da)003:1050: ma rung 'dod la ma chags shing //
NK011(da)003:1051: dam tshig la sdang dgra chen rnams //
NK011(da)003:1052: thugs rje byang sems ldan pa yis //
NK011(da)003:1053: ngo mthon stobs kyis bsgral bar bya //
NK011(da)003:1054: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sa pa ri w+aa
NK011(da)003:1055: ra ma h+aa rak+ta ma h+aa m+aam sa ma h+aa
NK011(da)003:1056: tsit+ta ma h+aa ba su ta ma h+aa go ro
NK011(da)003:1057: tsa na ma h+aa kem ni ri ti ma h+aa
NK011(da)003:1058: pany+tsa amri ta ma h+aa ar+g+ham pra t+aits+tsha hoh kha
NK011(da)003:1063: bdun pa sbyor sgrol gyi mchod la gnyis las /
NK011(da)003:1064: sgrol ba ni sngar dmigs bya dgug bstim byas pa'i ling ga mdun du bkod la /
NK011(da)003:1066: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)003:1067: sprul pa chen po'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)003:1068: phyag brnyan chen po'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)003:1069: shwa na mu kha'i bdag nyid chen po'i sa bdag
NK011(da)003:1070: chen mo'i khyed kyi phrin las mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i
NK011(da)003:1073: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed cing //
NK011(da)003:1074: dus gsum rgyal ba'i gdung 'tshob pa'i //
NK011(da)003:1075: rig 'dzin bdag cag rnams la ni //
NK011(da)003:1076: gnod cing gdug pa'i dgra dang bgegs //
NK011(da)003:1077: bdud dang bar du gcod pa rnams //
NK011(da)003:1078: khro bo chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK011(da)003:1079: yud tsam gyis ni 'dir bkug nas //
NK011(da)003:1080: mngon spyod tshul bzhin bsgral ba dang //
NK011(da)003:1081: lus ngag rdul du bshig nas kyang //
NK011(da)003:1082: sdug bsngal nyams su myong bar mdzod //
NK011(da)003:1083: lam h+aum lam s+t+wam b+ha ya nam /
NK011(da)003:1084: mo ha g+ha ta ya b+ha ga w+aa na h+r+aih
NK011(da)003:1085: kri bi kri badz+ra h+aum k+aa ra h+aum badz+ra k+ai
NK011(da)003:1086: li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum bam hohsarba big+h+nam badz+ra k+ai
NK011(da)003:1087: li k+ai la ya h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1088: ces bzla bzhin du phur bu bsgril zhing gdab /
NK011(da)003:1090: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK011(da)003:1091: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK011(da)003:1092: zungs shig rgyob cig rnam par chings //
NK011(da)003:1093: gtogs shig grogs dang bral ba gyis //
NK011(da)003:1094: rings par khug la smrar chug cig /
NK011(da)003:1095: phob cig rnam par gzir bar gyis //
NK011(da)003:1096: nga yi dbang du gyur nas kyang //
NK011(da)003:1097: bsgo ba'i bka' la 'dun par gyis //
NK011(da)003:1098: h+aum pa ra bid+ya ts+tshin+d+ha ts+tshin+d+ha h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1100: gri h+na gri h+na h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1101: ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1103: tra sa ya tra sa ya h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1104: ha sa ya ra ha sa ya ra hri dan+da h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1105: sh+r+ai g+h+ram a na ya h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1106: dz+wa la pa ya dz+wa la pa ya h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1107: a be sh+aa ya a be sh+aa ya h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1108: b+han+d+ha ya b+han+d+ha ya h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1110: bran dang bka' nyan pho nya'i tshogs //
NK011(da)003:1111: khyod kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK011(da)003:1112: sngon chad khas blang dam bca' bzhin //
NK011(da)003:1113: mngon spyod phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK011(da)003:1121: ka ta ka ta badz+ra ye /
NK011(da)003:1123: a dzi te a pa ra dzi te /
NK011(da)003:1124: m+aa ra se na pra mar+d+ha na h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1125: ces khro bcu'i phur pa rnams so sor gdab /
NK011(da)003:1126: rdo rje gsang ba'i bka' las ni //
NK011(da)003:1127: sdig can gang zhig 'da' byed pa //
NK011(da)003:1128: stobs chen khro bo chen po yis //
NK011(da)003:1129: klad pa tshal pa brgya ru khos //
NK011(da)003:1130: nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
NK011(da)003:1131: nga yi bka' las 'da' ma byed //
NK011(da)003:1132: h+aum ma ma pa sham ku ru ma tam nya
NK011(da)003:1133: ka ra i nan d+ha d+hi ma ma sh+r+ai g+h+ram
NK011(da)003:1135: ces mtshon cha sna tshogs kyi chab phab par bsam zhing ral gris gtub /
NK011(da)003:1136: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa yi //
NK011(da)003:1138: nga la bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK011(da)003:1139: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul med par byos //
NK011(da)003:1141: ta th+aa ya ta th+aa ya h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1142: ces steng 'og gi khro bo gnyis kyis spyi bo dang rkang mthil du gdab /
NK011(da)003:1144: rdungs shig rdo rje 'bar ba'i gtun //
NK011(da)003:1146: rdo rje me dpal snying bsregs nas //
NK011(da)003:1147: lus ngag rdul phran bzhin du rlog /
NK011(da)003:1148: rdo rje tho bas dgra bgegs rdul du brlag cing 'od zer 'phro bas bsregs par bsam mo //
NK011(da)003:1150: khro mo 'bar ba'i gtun khung du //
NK011(da)003:1151: rdo rje tho bas brdungs byas nas //
NK011(da)003:1152: lha yang rung steng brlag par 'gyur //
NK011(da)003:1153: kha tam kha tam kha tam /
NK011(da)003:1156: badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)003:1157: ha ha h+aum h+aum phata phata /
NK011(da)003:1158: ces yum gyi mkha' gru gsum du yab kyi rdo
NK011(da)003:1159: rje gtun shing gi sbyor bas dgra bgegs bsgral zhing
NK011(da)003:1160: rtog tshogs dbyings su dag par sbyor ba'o //
NK011(da)003:1162: dgra bgegs bsgral ba'i dmar chen gtor mar sbreng zhing /
NK011(da)003:1164: bla med mchog gi chod pa dam pa 'di //
NK011(da)003:1165: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer rnam par 'phro //
NK011(da)003:1166: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yis rab brgyan te //
NK011(da)003:1167: thugs dam bzhin las ci bder bzhes su gsol //
NK011(da)003:1168: dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka e dam push+pe /
NK011(da)003:1172: ba ling+ta p+au dza hoh pra t+aits+tsha kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)003:1174: badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)003:1175: zhes phul bas lha thams cad dgyes nas ha ha zhes bzhad /
NK011(da)003:1176: h+aum h+aum zhes gsungs nas bdag la byin gyis brlab /
NK011(da)003:1177: phata phata phata ces gsungs te dgra bgegs bsgral te chos nyid du gnas spar bar bsam mo //
NK011(da)003:1180: dpal ldan che ba'i che mchog lha yi lha //
NK011(da)003:1181: dus gsum bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK011(da)003:1182: phrin las thams cad rdzogs pa'i dpal chen po //
NK011(da)003:1183: he ru ka dpal khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)003:1184: gtum chen brjid pa 'gying zhing sgeg pa'i sku //
NK011(da)003:1185: bdud tshogs sder bcas 'dul ba'i dpa' bo che //
NK011(da)003:1186: mi sdug srin po khros 'dra'i cha lugs kyis //
NK011(da)003:1187: srid gsum gdug pa 'dul mdzad khyod la bstod //
NK011(da)003:1188: bzhad sgra 'brug stong ldir 'dra'i gad rgyangs can //
NK011(da)003:1189: drag shul chen pos ri rab thal bar rlog /
NK011(da)003:1190: 'jigs rung rtsal gyis khams gsum gcig tu sgrol //
NK011(da)003:1191: dpal chen khro bo'i dbang phyug khyod la bstod //
NK011(da)003:1192: snying rjes bsgrub pa'i dam tshig chen po yis //
NK011(da)003:1193: 'gro kun byang chub snying por 'dren mdzad cing //
NK011(da)003:1194: thugs rje dbyings nas khros pa'i rngams stabs kyis //
NK011(da)003:1195: 'khor ba gtan nas rlag byed khyod la bstod //
NK011(da)003:1196: gdug can drag pos 'dul bar nyer dgongs nas //
NK011(da)003:1197: 'bar ba'i khro tshul du mas gar mdzad kyang //
NK011(da)003:1198: chos dbyings zhi ba'i ngang las mi g.yo ba //
NK011(da)003:1199: dpal chen mngon rdzogs rgyal po khyod la bstod //
NK011(da)003:1200: nam mkha'i khams kun yongs su khyab pa'i sku //
NK011(da)003:1201: gling bzhi ri rab nyi zla gza' skar yang //
NK011(da)003:1202: sku yi rgyan du che ba dpal chen po //
NK011(da)003:1203: che btsan 'gran zla bral ba khyod la bstod //
NK011(da)003:1204: gnyen po ye shes gzhom gzhig mi mnga' bas //
NK011(da)003:1205: nyon mongs rtog pa'i bdud tshogs tshar gcod phyir //
NK011(da)003:1206: phyag g.yas rdo rje rtse dgu 'phyar ba yis //
NK011(da)003:1207: ri rab chen po kun kyang thal bar rlog /
NK011(da)003:1208: bdud dang 'byung po kun gyi klad pa 'gem //
NK011(da)003:1209: srid pa'i 'gong po spun dgu rdul du rlog /
NK011(da)003:1210: 'gro rnams theg pa dgu yi lam la 'dren //
NK011(da)003:1211: bar pa rdo rje rtse lnga bsnams pa yis //
NK011(da)003:1212: nyon mongs dug lnga gtan nas rlog byed cing //
NK011(da)003:1213: don dam spros med byang sems rnam pa lngas //
NK011(da)003:1214: rgyud lnga'i sems can thar pa'i lam la sbyor //
NK011(da)003:1215: bdud dang nag po'i phyogs rnams thams cad kun //
NK011(da)003:1216: kun tu bsdigs shing thal bar brlag bya'i phyir //
NK011(da)003:1217: dus mtha'i me ltar rab tu cher 'bar ba'i //
NK011(da)003:1218: ye shes me dpung 'bar ba'i sdigs mdzub gdengs //
NK011(da)003:1219: srid gsum gdug pa mtha' dag tshar bcad nas //
NK011(da)003:1220: dug gsum sku gsung thugs su sgrol byed cing //
NK011(da)003:1221: 'khor ba'i g.yul ngo gtan nas pham mdzad pa'i //
NK011(da)003:1222: dpa' bo rgyal rtags kha t+w+aam rtse gsum thogs //
NK011(da)003:1223: khro rgyal ma lus 'dus pa'i rtsal 'chang zhing //
NK011(da)003:1224: mi bzad stong khams bsreg pa'i me stag 'phro //
NK011(da)003:1225: btab na ye shes lha yang thal bar rlog /
NK011(da)003:1226: 'bar ba'i phreng ba 'khrigs pa'i 'od zer can //
NK011(da)003:1227: ri rab brjid pa'i phur pa drag tu 'dril //
NK011(da)003:1228: khams gsum yongs sgrol dpa' bo che la bstod //
NK011(da)003:1229: gar gyi dbang phyug rnam par 'gyur ba'i sku //
NK011(da)003:1230: dpal dang dur khrod chas rnams yongs rdzogs shing //
NK011(da)003:1231: zhabs bzhi brkyang bskum gyad kyi dor stabs kyis //
NK011(da)003:1232: dregs pa lha chen gnon mdzad khyod la bstod //
NK011(da)003:1234: 'jigs pa'i btsun mo 'khor lo rgyas 'debs ma //
NK011(da)003:1235: kun tu bzang mo dkyil 'khor kun gyi yum //
NK011(da)003:1236: gdug pa 'dul phyir srin mo khros pa'i gzugs //
NK011(da)003:1237: srid pa'i 'khor lo ye shes rgya yis 'debs //
NK011(da)003:1238: gnyis med don ldan yab la dgyes par 'khril //
NK011(da)003:1239: phyag g.yas 'khor los bdud kyi mgo lus gshog /
NK011(da)003:1240: g.yon pa thod khrag 'khor 'das dbang du sdud //
NK011(da)003:1241: 'jigs pa'i sku la phyag rgya lnga yis spras //
NK011(da)003:1242: drag po'i nga ros 'jig rten g.yo zhing 'khrug /
NK011(da)003:1243: rgyud lnga'i sems can thugs rjes dbyings su sgrol //
NK011(da)003:1244: srid gsum gdug pa'i tshogs rnams thal bar rlog /
NK011(da)003:1245: mkha' 'gro yongs kyi gtso mo khyod la bstod //
NK011(da)003:1247: phyogs bcu dregs pa bsnol ba'i gdan steng na //
NK011(da)003:1248: ye shes bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i sku //
NK011(da)003:1249: 'jigs byed 'bar ba'i khro rgyal chen po bcu //
NK011(da)003:1250: mi dge bcu spang dge bcu rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK011(da)003:1251: kun kyang zhal gsum phyag drug gtum la rngams //
NK011(da)003:1252: phyogs skyong dregs pa pho mo thams cad 'dul //
NK011(da)003:1253: dbu skra ral pa srid pa'i rtse mor 'bar //
NK011(da)003:1254: mi sdug khro gnyer smin pa g.yo ba can //
NK011(da)003:1255: spyan gsum dmar zlum sdang mig phyogs bcur gzigs //
NK011(da)003:1256: log par lta ba rtsad nas gcod cing sgrol //
NK011(da)003:1257: mche ba zangs yag skye shi rtsad nas gcod //
NK011(da)003:1258: gdugs can tshogs rnams sgrol ba'i phyag mtshan bsnams //
NK011(da)003:1259: dur khrod chas brgyad sku yi rgyan du che //
NK011(da)003:1260: rdo rje rin chen gshog pa nam mkhar gdengs //
NK011(da)003:1261: rngams pa'i zhal gdangs ljags 'dril rkan sgra sdeb //
NK011(da)003:1262: kun kyang phur bu sgril zhing phyogs bcur 'debs //
NK011(da)003:1263: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med yum dang 'khril //
NK011(da)003:1264: g.yas g.yon dag tu sprul pa'i phra thabs ni //
NK011(da)003:1265: mgo brnyan mche gshog rdzu 'phrul mthu stobs can //
NK011(da)003:1266: 'bar ba'i khro rgyal ma bcos rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK011(da)003:1267: sgra las 'das pa grags stong h+aum sgra gsung //
NK011(da)003:1268: bsam dang bral ba sgrol byed snying rje'i ngang //
NK011(da)003:1269: yon tan phrin las thams cad rdzogs pa'i dpal //
NK011(da)003:1270: sprul pa chen po'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)003:1272: gnyis med sku la 'khril ba'i gzungs mchog ma //
NK011(da)003:1273: rngams brjid 'jigs pa khro bo'i cha lugs can //
NK011(da)003:1274: pha rol phyin pa bcu yi ngo bo nyid //
NK011(da)003:1275: bdud 'dul yum gyi tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)003:1277: rdo rje gdong mo pho nya mgyogs ma bzhi //
NK011(da)003:1278: dgra bgegs gdug pa 'gug 'ching sdom zhing rdeg /
NK011(da)003:1279: shar lho nub byang sgo srung drag shul can //
NK011(da)003:1280: sgo ma chen mo bzhi la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)003:1282: mthing nag gru gsum 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor na //
NK011(da)003:1283: dpal gyi sras mchog 'jigs byed k+ai la ya //
NK011(da)003:1284: mthing nag khros pa zhal gcig phyag bzhi pa //
NK011(da)003:1285: phyag g.yas dang po s+t+wa gri ltag par 'phyar //
NK011(da)003:1286: 'og ma rdo rje ri rab gnon stabs 'dzin //
NK011(da)003:1287: g.yon pa'i phyag na kha t+w+aam ka 'khrol zhing //
NK011(da)003:1288: 'og mas phur bu dgra bgegs snying la 'debs //
NK011(da)003:1289: rigs lngas dbu brgyan thugs srog h+aum du 'bar //
NK011(da)003:1290: snyan nas 'brug sgrog spyan nas me 'od 'phro //
NK011(da)003:1291: shangs nas rlung 'tshub zhal nas thog ser 'bebs //
NK011(da)003:1292: mche ba gtsigs shing ag tshom me ltar 'bar //
NK011(da)003:1293: khyod kyi lte ba man chad chas rnams ni //
NK011(da)003:1294: lcags phur zur gsum me stag phyogs bcur 'phro //
NK011(da)003:1295: dgra bgegs gdug pa'i tshogs rnams skad cig sgrol //
NK011(da)003:1296: mi g.yo che mchog sku gsung thugs kyi ngang //
NK011(da)003:1297: khro rgyal 'dus pa'i sras mchog k+ai la ya //
NK011(da)003:1298: srid par 'khyams pa'i sems can thams cad kun //
NK011(da)003:1299: thabs kyis bsgral ba'i skal dang mi ldan yang //
NK011(da)003:1300: shugs kyis sgrol ba'i phrin las mdzad slad du //
NK011(da)003:1301: dbyer med sku gsung thugs su sgrol mdzad pa //
NK011(da)003:1302: sras mchog k+ai la ya la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)003:1304: bcu pa dzapa bsnyen 'bul ba la gsum ste /
NK011(da)003:1305: rang gi gnas sbyang ba dang /
NK011(da)003:1306: bzlas brjod bsnyen pa'i 'phro 'dus ye shes kyi lha nye bar bsnyen pa dang /
NK011(da)003:1307: gsang ba byang sems kyi dngos grub yum gyi mkha' las blang ba'o //
NK011(da)003:1309: dag nyid dpal chen por gsal ba'i thugs rin po
NK011(da)003:1310: che zur brgyad pa'i dbus su gzhal yas khang ga'u
NK011(da)003:1311: zur brgyad pa dbus dang zur brgyad la nyi gdan
NK011(da)003:1312: re / dbus kyi gdan la mthing nag zur brgyad kyi shar du badz+ra smug mdog /
NK011(da)003:1313: lhor k+ai li k+ai la ya ser po /
NK011(da)003:1317: lho nub tu h+aum ser po /
NK011(da)003:1318: nub byang du h+aum dkar po /
NK011(da)003:1319: byang shar du phata dmar po rnams 'bru brgyad kyis bskor ba /
NK011(da)003:1320: ljags kyi dkyil du pam las pad+ma 'dab brgyad kyi
NK011(da)003:1321: dbus dang 'dab rer yig 'bru dgu po rnams gsal
NK011(da)003:1323: skye med dbyings las 'bar ba'i skur snang ba //
NK011(da)003:1324: 'jigs byed chen po dpal chen he ru ka /
NK011(da)003:1325: thugs kyi dpal be'u rin chen ga'u la /
NK011(da)003:1326: yi ge 'bru dgu don gyi phra bkod pa //
NK011(da)003:1327: ljags kyi pad+ma'i 'bru dgu dang bcas la //
NK011(da)003:1328: rnam gsum dus gcig yid la gsal gyur nas //
NK011(da)003:1329: chos nyid rdo rje gsum gyi glur blangs pas //
NK011(da)003:1330: a ni ma skyes don gyi gsung du rig /
NK011(da)003:1331: yid kyi sngags tshig bar chad med par bzla //
NK011(da)003:1332: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1334: ye shes lha tshogs spyan 'dren gshegs //
NK011(da)003:1337: / tsit+ta rin chen zur brgyad kyi //
NK011(da)003:1338: gsang chen thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK011(da)003:1339: byang chub sems kyi yig 'bru dgu //
NK011(da)003:1340: gu h+ya gsang ba'i lam du byung //
NK011(da)003:1342: gsang ba'i yi ge h+aum gis drangs //
NK011(da)003:1344: bsnol mar bstim nas tshogs chen rdzogs //
NK011(da)003:1345: slar yang thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK011(da)003:1347: rigs lnga yab kyi sku la thim //
NK011(da)003:1349: stong khams gang nas thugs kar 'dus //
NK011(da)003:1350: thugs ka'i dpal be'u zur brgyad kyi //
NK011(da)003:1352: gong bzhin bzlas shing mchod pa'o //
NK011(da)003:1355: bdag nyid thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK011(da)003:1356: ye shes sems dpa' he ru ka /
NK011(da)003:1357: khro bo'i tshul du gsal ba yi //
NK011(da)003:1358: de yi thugs kyi dkyil 'khor ni //
NK011(da)003:1359: dpal be'u rin chen zur brgyad pa //
NK011(da)003:1360: yi ge 'bru dgu'i pra bkod de //
NK011(da)003:1361: spro zhing bsdu ba'i 'od zer ni //
NK011(da)003:1362: gser gyi ba thag gzengs pa bzhin //
NK011(da)003:1363: spros pas stong khams yongs su khyab //
NK011(da)003:1364: slar bsdus dpal gyi be'u bkang //
NK011(da)003:1367: bdag nyid dpal gyi dkyil 'khor na //
NK011(da)003:1368: ye shes sems dpa' he ru ka'i //
NK011(da)003:1369: yid bzhin rin chen zur brgyad par //
NK011(da)003:1370: yi ge 'bru dgu'i phra bkod de //
NK011(da)003:1371: thugs nas ljags kyi dkyil du spros //
NK011(da)003:1372: 'brug gi sgra ltar rab grags pas //
NK011(da)003:1373: gdug pa'i tshogs rnams zil gyis mnan //
NK011(da)003:1375: bsnyen pa'i dus na rgyang mi ring //
NK011(da)003:1376: bsgrub pa'i dus na mthu ma chung //
NK011(da)003:1377: de ltar gsal ba'i lha tshogs rnams //
NK011(da)003:1378: gnyis med dbyings kyi ngang du thim //
NK011(da)003:1383: byang chub sems kyi dngos grub mchog /
NK011(da)003:1384: chags pa'i bdag nyid dpal gyi yum //
NK011(da)003:1385: yum gyi mkha' las byung ba de //
NK011(da)003:1386: skye shi med pa'i khrag chen 'di //
NK011(da)003:1387: 'dod pa'i dbang mo yum gyi mkha' //
NK011(da)003:1388: sangs rgyas kun gyi skyed mo'i tshal //
NK011(da)003:1389: gru gsum dgyes pa'i pho brang mchog /
NK011(da)003:1390: a las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK011(da)003:1391: byang chub sems ni e ru snang //
NK011(da)003:1392: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gsang sbubs gang //
NK011(da)003:1393: ye shes rdo rje rtse lnga par //
NK011(da)003:1394: byang chub sems ni dkar po //
NK011(da)003:1395: ga bur shel gyi dkyil 'khor te //
NK011(da)003:1396: dang lam gyis byin brlabs nas //
NK011(da)003:1397: dkar dmar bsnol mar bstim pa las //
NK011(da)003:1401: gnyis med 'khril ba'i phyag rgya las //
NK011(da)003:1403: mgal me klad la bskor ba bzhin //
NK011(da)003:1404: rdo rje rtse lnga'i gsang sbubs nas //
NK011(da)003:1406: sku yi gsang brgyud shangs nas phyungs //
NK011(da)003:1407: thabs chen yab kyi shangs su thim //
NK011(da)003:1408: sku mchog phyag rgya'i gsang bar drangs //
NK011(da)003:1409: ye shes rdo rje'i lam du phyungs //
NK011(da)003:1410: pad+ma'i gzhal yas khang du spro //
NK011(da)003:1411: mgal me klad la bskor ba bzhin //
NK011(da)003:1412: rgyun mi 'chad par bsgoms par bya //
NK011(da)003:1413: bde gshegs kun gyi sku gsung thugs //
NK011(da)003:1414: yi ge 'bru dgu'i phyag rgyar gsal //
NK011(da)003:1415: dngos grub rnam gsum tshul bzhin blangs //
NK011(da)003:1416: thams cad bde chen dbyings su rdzogs //
NK011(da)003:1417: mtshan ma'i spros dang bral bar bzla //
NK011(da)003:1418: gong bzhin bzlas mthar stong tshig gis mchod bshags bya zhing /
NK011(da)003:1419: khro bcu dang srung ma'i sngags dbang mo la b+h+yo bdun tshan bzhi rnams kyang ci rigs par bazla'o //
NK011(da)003:1420: gsum pa rjees kyi bya ba la /
NK011(da)003:1421: tshogs bshams byin brlab spyan drangs mchod //
NK011(da)003:1422: rol lhag brtan skyong las bzhi'i bro //
NK011(da)003:1423: dngos grub bzod gsol nyer bsdu dang //
NK011(da)003:1424: rgyun ting bsngo smon shis brjod do //
NK011(da)003:1425: zhes pa ltar bcu bzhi las /
NK011(da)003:1427: zhing ngam gcan gzan gyi pags pa'i steng du dam
NK011(da)003:1428: rdzas su 'os pa'i yo byad ci 'byor par bsham
NK011(da)003:1429: mo // gnyis pa byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK011(da)003:1431: badz+ra a mri ta kun+da l+ai ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1432: bi shud+d+he a mri ta h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1433: d+harma a mri ta h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1439: tshogs gzhong rin po che'i mchod sdong 'dab ma stong
NK011(da)003:1440: ldan gyi snying por tshogs rdzas rnams nyi zla pad+ma'i
NK011(da)003:1441: dkyil 'khor la gnas pa'i h+aum mthing kha +aam dmar
NK011(da)003:1442: po dkar po rnams kyis mtshan pa 'od du zhu
NK011(da)003:1443: ba las stong nyid kyi dbyings su gyur cing bdud
NK011(da)003:1444: rtsir zhu nas 'dod yon lnga'i rang bzhin du gyur
NK011(da)003:1446: gsum pa tshogs zhing spyan 'dren pa ni /
NK011(da)003:1448: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro dang //
NK011(da)003:1449: rdo rje gzhon nu yab yum sras //
NK011(da)003:1450: khro bo'i rgyal po mtha' yas pa //
NK011(da)003:1451: ma mo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs dang bcas //
NK011(da)003:1452: lha dang lha min rnal 'byor rnams //
NK011(da)003:1453: thugs dang mthun pa'i gnas mchog 'dir //
NK011(da)003:1454: dam tshig tshul bzhin gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)003:1455: kun bzang mchod sprin rol par mdzod //
NK011(da)003:1456: dam tshig bzhin du ci bder bzhes //
NK011(da)003:1457: dzahh+aum bam hoh bzhi pa mchod pa la spyi dang khyad par gnyis /
NK011(da)003:1458: dang po spyir mchod pa la lnga las /
NK011(da)003:1459: dang po mchod sprin spro ba ni /
NK011(da)003:1461: phyogs bcu dus gsum rgyal ba mchod pa dang //
NK011(da)003:1462: rnal 'byor dbang phyug thugs dam bskang ba'i phyir //
NK011(da)003:1463: sgo gsum g.yo sgyu med cing gus ldan pas //
NK011(da)003:1464: yo ga gsang ba'i mchod pa'i rnam grangs 'bul //
NK011(da)003:1465: snang srid chos dang rgyal srid rin po che //
NK011(da)003:1466: phyag rgya bzhi dang nyon mongs rnam pa lnga //
NK011(da)003:1467: ting 'dzin chos dang bdud rtsi rnam pa lnga //
NK011(da)003:1468: 'dod pa'i yon tan mang po glu dang gar //
NK011(da)003:1469: rtog med don gyi mchod pa la sogs 'bul //
NK011(da)003:1470: pho brang bzhugs gnas zhing khams thams cad du //
NK011(da)003:1471: mchod pa'i sprin gyis gtibs shing rgyas gyur cig /
NK011(da)003:1472: gnyis pa snang srid tshogs kyi mchod par bsngo ba ni /
NK011(da)003:1474: ye shes khro bo rol pa'i zhal chen por //
NK011(da)003:1475: snod bcud ma lus mchod pa chen por sbyor //
NK011(da)003:1476: dbyings dang ye shes rol pa'i mchod pa ru //
NK011(da)003:1477: so sor phye ste snod bcud mchod par 'bul //
NK011(da)003:1478: gsum pa kun tu dbyer med pa'i mchod pa ni /
NK011(da)003:1480: rgyal ba ma lus ye shes khro bo'i sku //
NK011(da)003:1481: dwangs snyigs mi phyed gnyis med mnyam pa'i ngang //
NK011(da)003:1482: dug gsum skyon bral dbyings kyi mchod pa 'di //
NK011(da)003:1483: 'du 'bral med pa srid gsum mchod par rol //
NK011(da)003:1484: bzhi pa thams cad mnyam pa nyid kyi mchod pa ni /
NK011(da)003:1486: mtha' dang dbus med mnyam pa'i mchod pa ni //
NK011(da)003:1487: nga dang bdag med mkha' ltar dag pa yi //
NK011(da)003:1488: ye shes lhun gyis grub pa'i mchod pa 'di //
NK011(da)003:1489: gnyis med bde chen mnyam pa'i mchod par rol //
NK011(da)003:1490: lnga pa 'dod yon gyi mchod pa ni /
NK011(da)003:1492: snying po byang chub rol rtsal longs sprul sku //
NK011(da)003:1493: 'dod pa'i yon tan lha mo'i mchod pa 'di //
NK011(da)003:1494: snang srid ma lus 'dod dgur bsgyur byas te //
NK011(da)003:1495: mkha' ltar dag pa'i dbyings su ye shes rol //
NK011(da)003:1497: gnyis pa khyad par du mchod pa la /
NK011(da)003:1498: mchod bshags bsgral stob gsum ste /
NK011(da)003:1499: tshogs phud rim pa gsum du spros la dang po mchod pa ni /
NK011(da)003:1501: rang byung ma bcos dbyings dang kha dog bral //
NK011(da)003:1502: rnam par rtog pa nyon mongs cir snang yang //
NK011(da)003:1503: gdod nas dag pas 'khor ba dbyings su rdzogs //
NK011(da)003:1504: ye shes khro rgyal thugs dam bskang ba'i phyir //
NK011(da)003:1505: khams gsum ma lus 'dus pa'i mchod pa 'di //
NK011(da)003:1506: dkyil 'khor lha tshogs zhal du bstab bo bzhes //
NK011(da)003:1507: gu ru d+he wa d+aa ki ni ma h+aa g+aa na tsa kra kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)003:1508: ma h+aa dza gad kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)003:1509: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)003:1511: ma h+aa m+aam sa kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)003:1513: ma h+aa ba su ta kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)003:1514: ma h+aa kem ni ri ti kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)003:1515: ma h+aa go ro tsa na kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)003:1516: ma h+aa sarba p+au dza hoh bar pa bshags pa ni /
NK011(da)003:1517: thog med dus nas da ltar thug gi bar //
NK011(da)003:1518: ma rig dbang gis dam las 'gal gyur te //
NK011(da)003:1519: lus kyi sdig byas spyod pa ngan du spyad //
NK011(da)003:1520: ngag gi tshig 'khyal smra ba ngan du brjod //
NK011(da)003:1521: sems kyi blo nor log par bsam pa sogs //
NK011(da)003:1522: 'dod khro gti mug dbang gis nongs bgyis pa //
NK011(da)003:1523: bkra ba'i lha tshogs khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK011(da)003:1524: ye shes lha la rtog pa mi mnga' yang //
NK011(da)003:1525: de yi 'khor du gtogs pa'i lha srin rnams //
NK011(da)003:1526: mi yi skyon mthong tsam na bar chad rtsol //
NK011(da)003:1527: 'gal 'khrul nongs pa ci mchis mthol lo bshags //
NK011(da)003:1528: bzod par bzhes nas tshangs pa stsal du gsol //
NK011(da)003:1530: tha ma bsgral ba la phur bu bca' zhing lhar gsal ba /
NK011(da)003:1533: dang po ni brub khung du ling+ga bcas la gdab phur gcig gam /
NK011(da)003:1535: bco lnga la sogs pa mdun du bkod la /
NK011(da)003:1536: badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum k+aa ra h+aum /
NK011(da)003:1537: sogs khro bu'i sngags rnams tshang bar brjod la /
NK011(da)003:1538: phur pa'i rgya mdud gong 'og gcum gzhogs la //
NK011(da)003:1539: khro bcu yab yum rang rang khra thabs bcas //
NK011(da)003:1540: zur bzhir sgo ma dpal la dam can rnams //
NK011(da)003:1541: gsal ba'i gnas gsum yi ge gsum gyis mtshan //
NK011(da)003:1542: de la 'od 'phros ye shes spyan drangs nas //
NK011(da)003:1543: mchod pas dgyes mchod gnyis su med par bstim //
NK011(da)003:1545: badz+ra sa ma dzah ma h+aa p+au dza hoh dzahh+aum bam hohganyisa pa sprul pa spro ba ni /
NK011(da)003:1546: h+aum h+aum h+aum bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la
NK011(da)003:1547: man+da la phata phata phata ha la ha la h+aum
NK011(da)003:1548: / bdag gi thugs las sprul pa'i khro bo ni //
NK011(da)003:1549: khro bo 'chol ba dpag tu med pa byung //
NK011(da)003:1550: srid pas gar khyab gnam sa bar snang kun //
NK011(da)003:1551: ras bal rlung gis gtor bzhin khyab par gyur //
NK011(da)003:1553: bden stobs brjod pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK011(da)003:1554: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya /
NK011(da)003:1555: dgra bgegs gnod byed dzah h+aum bam hoh zhes bkug ste ling+ga la bstim mo //
NK011(da)003:1557: gab pa'i sngags drug gis dgug gzhug bya ba dang /
NK011(da)003:1560: lha phral gzugs la dbab pa dang //
NK011(da)003:1561: byad du gzhug dang smyo ru gzhug /
NK011(da)003:1562: rdul du brlag dang zhal du stob //
NK011(da)003:1563: zhes pa'i dang po lha dang dbral ba ni /
NK011(da)003:1566: sras mchog phyag na gu gul bsnams //
NK011(da)003:1567: dgra bgegs 'go ba'i lha dang phrol //
NK011(da)003:1568: skyob pa'i grogs dang bral bar gyis //
NK011(da)003:1569: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)003:1570: sprul pa chen po'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)003:1571: phyag brnyan chen po'i shwa na mu kha'i dus la
