NK011(da)003:1572: bdag nyid chen po'i sa bdag chen mo'i khyod kyi
NK011(da)003:1573: phrin las mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)003:1574: rdo rje gsang ba'i bka' las ni //
NK011(da)003:1575: sdig can gang zhig 'da' byed pa //
NK011(da)003:1576: stobs chen khro bo chen po yis //
NK011(da)003:1577: klad pa tshal pa brgya ru khos //
NK011(da)003:1578: nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
NK011(da)003:1579: nga yi bka' las 'da' ma byed //
NK011(da)003:1580: gtogs shing grogs dang bral bar gyis //
NK011(da)003:1581: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya /
NK011(da)003:1582: dgra bgegs ha sa ya ra ha sa ya ra h+aihdan+da h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1583: sras mchog de yi thugs ka nas //
NK011(da)003:1584: rang 'dra dpag med thon nas kyang //
NK011(da)003:1585: gu gul sbyar ba'i dud sprin gyis //
NK011(da)003:1586: dgra bgegs 'go ba'i lha kun byer //
NK011(da)003:1587: kho rang gcig pur 'khyams par gyur //
NK011(da)003:1588: gnyis pa gzugs la dbab pa ni /
NK011(da)003:1589: lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK011(da)003:1591: sras mchog phyag na lcags kyu thogs //
NK011(da)003:1592: dgra bgegs rnam shes rten la phob //
NK011(da)003:1594: rdo rje gsang ba'i sogs tshig rkang drug gi rjes su /
NK011(da)003:1595: phob cig rnam par gzir bar gyis //
NK011(da)003:1596: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dgra bgegs a we sha ya a we sha ya h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1597: sras mchog de yi thugs ka nas //
NK011(da)003:1598: rang 'dra dpag med thon nas kyang //
NK011(da)003:1599: h+aum dang phata kyi sgra sgrog cing //
NK011(da)003:1600: lcags kyus zung la mtshon chas bsdigs //
NK011(da)003:1601: skad cig yud la bkug nas bstim //
NK011(da)003:1602: gsum pa byad du gzhug pa ni /
NK011(da)003:1603: tshon skud dang yugs skras yan lag rnams bcing ba'i tshul bya zhing /
NK011(da)003:1605: sras mchog phyag na zhags pa thogs //
NK011(da)003:1606: dgra bgegs lus ngag dam du sdoms //
NK011(da)003:1608: rdo rje gsang ba'i sogs tshig drug gi rjes su /
NK011(da)003:1609: zungs shig chings shig rnam par sdoms //
NK011(da)003:1610: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dgra bgegs dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai g+h+ram a na ya h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1611: sras mchog de yi thugs ka nas //
NK011(da)003:1612: rang 'dra dpag med thon nas kyang //
NK011(da)003:1613: nyams pa'i dgra bgegs lus kyi cha //
NK011(da)003:1614: gru gu thul du bcings par gyur //
NK011(da)003:1615: bzhi pa smyo ru gzhug pa ni /
NK011(da)003:1616: dug sna tshogs dang d+ha du ra'i khu bas brab cing /
NK011(da)003:1618: sras mchog phyag na dug thun thogs //
NK011(da)003:1619: dgra bgegs smyo zhing 'bog tu chugs //
NK011(da)003:1620: bab brgyad dang tshig drug gi rjes su /
NK011(da)003:1621: rings par khug la smrar chug cig /
NK011(da)003:1622: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dgra bgegs dz+wa la pa ya dz+wa la pa ya h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1623: dgra bgegs smyo zhing 'bogs nas kyang //
NK011(da)003:1624: ci byas thol thol smra bar gyur //
NK011(da)003:1625: lnga pa rdul du brlag pa ni /
NK011(da)003:1628: sras mchog phyag na tho ba thogs //
NK011(da)003:1629: dgra bgegs lus ngag rdul du rlog /
NK011(da)003:1630: bab brgyad dang tshig drug gi rjes su /
NK011(da)003:1631: lus ngag rdul phran bzhin du rlog /
NK011(da)003:1632: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dgra bgegs ta th+aa ya ta th+aa ya h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1633: sra mchog tho ba thogs pa yis //
NK011(da)003:1634: dgra bgegs nyil nyil 'dres par brdungs //
NK011(da)003:1635: drug pa zhal du bstabs pa ni phur gdab byas pa'i rjes su 'brel bas 'og tu ston no //
NK011(da)003:1636: gnyis pa bsgral las dngos la drug gi dang po kun gzhi rtsad nas bcad de sgrol ba ni /
NK011(da)003:1637: de yang bdag dpal chen po /
NK011(da)003:1639: ling+ga gnod byed kun 'dus su gsal bas phur bu bsgril zhing /
NK011(da)003:1641: srid pa'i phur bu sgrub pa dang //
NK011(da)003:1642: dbang dang dngos grub blang ba'i phyir //
NK011(da)003:1643: ye shes khro bo gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)003:1644: khro bo chen po gshegs nas kyang //
NK011(da)003:1645: rtags dang mtshan ma bstan pa dang //
NK011(da)003:1646: k+ai la ya yi dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)003:1648: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed cing //
NK011(da)003:1649: dus gsum rgyal ba'i gdung 'tsho ba pa'i //
NK011(da)003:1650: rig 'dzin bdag cag rnams la ni //
NK011(da)003:1651: gnod byed gdug pa'i dgra dang bgegs //
NK011(da)003:1652: bdud dang bar du gcod pa rnams //
NK011(da)003:1653: khro bo chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK011(da)003:1654: yud tsam gyis ni 'dir khug la //
NK011(da)003:1655: mngon spyod tshul bzhin bsgral ba dang //
NK011(da)003:1656: lus ngag rdul bzhin bshig nas kyang //
NK011(da)003:1657: sdug bsngal nyams su myong bar mdzod //
NK011(da)003:1658: lam h+aum lam stam+b+ha ya nan mo ha g+ha ta
NK011(da)003:1659: ya b+ha ga w+aa na h+r+aihkri bi kri badz+ra h+aum
NK011(da)003:1660: k+aa ra h+aum badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum
NK011(da)003:1661: bam hoh sarba big+h+n+aam badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya
NK011(da)003:1662: h+aum phata / badz+ra h+aum k+aa ra h+aum phata h+aum k+aa ra h+aum a phata /
NK011(da)003:1663: ces bzla bzhin du phur bu snying gar gdab /
NK011(da)003:1664: de yang tshe khrus kyi dgongs pa la /
NK011(da)003:1667: dkyil 'khor gsum gyi gnas gsum a dkar las //
NK011(da)003:1668: a dkar 'od zer phra mo grangs med 'phros //
NK011(da)003:1669: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad spyan drangs te //
NK011(da)003:1670: a yi rang bzhin nyid du thams cad zhu //
NK011(da)003:1671: bdag nyid khro bo phur bu la thim pas //
NK011(da)003:1672: lus ngag yid kyi shes bya'i sgrib pa sbyangs //
NK011(da)003:1673: phyag rgya chen por gsal te bdag gi khrus //
NK011(da)003:1675: bdag gi gnas gsum a las 'od 'phros pas //
NK011(da)003:1676: rgyal ba mchod cing 'gro drug sdig sgrib sbyangs //
NK011(da)003:1677: srid gsum a yi rang bzhin byang chub sems //
NK011(da)003:1678: 'od kyi gong bur gsal te snang srid khrus //
NK011(da)003:1679: a rnams byang sems gyur te 'od gsal bar //
NK011(da)003:1680: mtha' nas rim gyi 'dus te gzas po yi //
NK011(da)003:1681: sgo gsum thim nas lus ngag yid gsum sbyangs //
NK011(da)003:1682: a yi rang bzhin byang chub sems su zhu //
NK011(da)003:1683: 'od kyi gong bur gyur te gzas po'i khrus //
NK011(da)003:1684: de ltar khrus lung rnam pa gsum po rdzogs //
NK011(da)003:1687: gzas po'i snying dkyil pad 'dab bzhir gyes pa'i /
NK011(da)003:1688: bzhi mdor rtsa yi dwangs ma 'dus de'i nang //
NK011(da)003:1689: khrag gi dwangs ma byi'u'i mgo bo tsam //
NK011(da)003:1690: de la dbug dang 'od kyi dwangs ma gnas //
NK011(da)003:1691: 'od kyi thag pa tshe tshad dang mnyam zhing //
NK011(da)003:1692: ba thag lta bur d+r+wa bas bstums te gnas //
NK011(da)003:1693: de rnams dbus su rnam shes 'od du gnas //
NK011(da)003:1695: phur bu'i 'od kyis pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi //
NK011(da)003:1696: bya sgro mer tshud lta bur thul gyis bsregs //
NK011(da)003:1697: 'byung ba bzhi la btab pa zhes bya'o //
NK011(da)003:1698: rtsa bzhi chon thag bsdus pa bzhin du gyur //
NK011(da)003:1699: de ni 'byung ba'i rgyu bzhir btab pa'o //
NK011(da)003:1700: rtsa bzhi'i dwangs ma 'dus pa phur rtse la //
NK011(da)003:1701: sbrul 'khyil lta bur hril gyis 'khril gyur nas //
NK011(da)003:1702: des ni rgyu bzhi'i dwangs ma zhe sdang bcad //
NK011(da)003:1703: de yi dbugs rta drod kyi dwangs ma de //
NK011(da)003:1704: me la chu blug bzhin du zhi gyur cing //
NK011(da)003:1705: dbugs kyi rta bsgral phrag dog rtsad bcad pa'o //
NK011(da)003:1706: de la 'od kyi dwangs ma chags pa de //
NK011(da)003:1707: khab len rdo bzhin phur bu la 'dus pas //
NK011(da)003:1708: rdo tshan kha ba bab ltar skam par bsam //
NK011(da)003:1709: sems kyi yul phyung nga rgyal rtsad bcad pa'o //
NK011(da)003:1710: de yi khrag gi dwangs ma sbal pa ni //
NK011(da)003:1711: lcags bsreg chu thig phog bzhin skam par bsgom //
NK011(da)003:1712: dwangs ma gnas sleb 'dod chags rtsad bcad pa'o //
NK011(da)003:1713: tshe skud ba thag d+r+wa bas bstums pa de //
NK011(da)003:1714: r+ts+wa phung me lce 'phrad pa lta bur tshig /
NK011(da)003:1715: tshe yi rten phral gti mug rtsad bcad pa'o //
NK011(da)003:1716: de rnams dbus kyi tshe yi rten gyur pa //
NK011(da)003:1717: a zhes brjod pas ar gyur phur rtser sbyang //
NK011(da)003:1719: bo d+hi tsit+ta +aah bo d+hi tsit+ta h+aum /
NK011(da)003:1721: bdag la thim pas bdag nyid lhag par yang //
NK011(da)003:1722: sku gsung thugs kyi gzi byin cher rgyas te //
NK011(da)003:1723: phyag rgya chen po'i ngang du gnas pa ni //
NK011(da)003:1724: bkrag mdangs 'phrog pa bdag gi tshe lung go //
NK011(da)003:1725: kho yi rnam shes bdag gi thugs ka ru //
NK011(da)003:1726: a ru gnas pa tshigs pa'i lam la phyungs //
NK011(da)003:1727: rlung sgrom shangs nas dung khang gzhal yas song //
NK011(da)003:1728: sgal tshigs rta brgyud rdo rje'i lam nas phyungs //
NK011(da)003:1729: 'khor lo rgyas 'debs yum gyi mkha' ru babs //
NK011(da)003:1730: h+aum gsum gyur pa phata gsum gyis 'phangs pas //
NK011(da)003:1731: 'og min rgyal ba rigs lnga'i sbyor mtshams thim //
NK011(da)003:1732: h+aum de rdo rje de las rdo rje sems //
NK011(da)003:1733: ye shes rang bzhin byas pa kho'i tshe lung //
NK011(da)003:1734: zhes tshe khrus kyi dgongs pa zab bo //
NK011(da)003:1735: de dag ngag tu brjod pa'am /
NK011(da)003:1736: ma brjod kyang don bsam pa gal che'o //
NK011(da)003:1737: de nas mtshon cha'i char 'bab par bsam la /
NK011(da)003:1739: gnyis pa nyon mongs pa skye ba'i sgo lnga dag par bsgral ba ni /
NK011(da)003:1740: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK011(da)003:1741: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK011(da)003:1742: zungs shig rgyob cig rnam par chings //
NK011(da)003:1743: gtogs shing grogs dang bral bar gyis //
NK011(da)003:1744: rings par khug la smrar chug cig /
NK011(da)003:1745: phob cig rnam par gzir bar gyis //
NK011(da)003:1746: nga yi dbang du gyur nas kyang //
NK011(da)003:1747: bsgo ba'i bka' la nyan par byos //
NK011(da)003:1748: h+aum pa ra bid+y+aa ts+tshin+d+ha ts+tshin+d+ha h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1751: ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1753: tra sha ya tra sha ya h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1754: ha sa ya ra ha sa ya ra h+r+aihdan+da h'u phata /
NK011(da)003:1755: sh+r+ai g+h+ram +aa na ya h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1756: dz+wa la pa ya dz+wa la pa ya h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1757: +aa be sha ya a be sha ya h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1758: b+han+d+ha ya b+han+d+ha ya h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1759: ces brjod cing khro bo so so'i phur bu yod
NK011(da)003:1760: na dang gcig las med kyang de dang der mos
NK011(da)003:1761: la gnas so sor gdab bo //
NK011(da)003:1762: gsum pa tshogs brgyad dag par bsgral ba ni /
NK011(da)003:1763: bran dang bka' nyan pho nya'i tshogs //
NK011(da)003:1764: khyod kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK011(da)003:1765: sngon chad khas blangs dam bcas pas //
NK011(da)003:1766: mngon spyod phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK011(da)003:1774: ka ta ka ta badz+ra ye /
NK011(da)003:1776: a dzi te a pa ra dzi te /
NK011(da)003:1777: m+aa ra se na pra mar+d+ha ni h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1778: ces sngar bzhin khro bo bcu'i phur bu gnas so sor gdab bo //
NK011(da)003:1779: bzhi pa dge sdig cha mnyam ste bsgral ba ni /
NK011(da)003:1780: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa yi //
NK011(da)003:1782: nga la bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK011(da)003:1783: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul med par byos //
NK011(da)003:1784: sarba a na ya h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1785: ta th+aa ya ta th+aa ya h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1786: ces steng 'og gi phur bu spyi gtsug dang rkang
NK011(da)003:1787: mthil du btab pas 'khor 'das kyi mtha' bsal lo
NK011(da)003:1788: // lnga pa ma bdud kyi dmod pas bsgral ba ni /
NK011(da)003:1789: rdo rje gsang ba'i bka' las ni //
NK011(da)003:1790: sdig can gang zhig 'da' byed pa //
NK011(da)003:1791: stobs chen khro bo chen po yis //
NK011(da)003:1792: klad pa tshal pa brgya ru khos //
NK011(da)003:1793: nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
NK011(da)003:1794: nga yi bka' las 'da' ma byed //
NK011(da)003:1795: h+aum ma ma p+aa sham ku ru ma tam nya
NK011(da)003:1796: ka ra i nan d+ha d+hi ma m+aa sh+r+ai g+h+ram
NK011(da)003:1798: ces dpral ba nas ltag pa dang /
NK011(da)003:1801: g.yon nas g.yas rnams su thal phyung du btab ste dbang po rnams kyi rten med par byas la /
NK011(da)003:1803: drug pa gtun du brdung ste bsgral ba ni /
NK011(da)003:1805: brdungs shig rdo rje 'bar ba'i gtun //
NK011(da)003:1807: rdo rje me dbal snying bsregs nas //
NK011(da)003:1808: lus ngag rdul phran bzhin du rlog /
NK011(da)003:1809: khro mo 'bar ba'i gtun khung du //
NK011(da)003:1810: rdo rje tho bas brdungs byas nas //
NK011(da)003:1811: lha yang rung ste bsgral bar bya //
NK011(da)003:1812: bcol ba'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK011(da)003:1813: kha tam kha tam kha tam /
NK011(da)003:1816: ces tho gtun yab yum gyi mkha' gsang dbyings rig
NK011(da)003:1817: gi sbyor bas gzugs phung zag med kyi dbyings su
NK011(da)003:1818: bcom par bsam la tho bas brdung zhing kha t+w+aam
NK011(da)003:1819: gyi phyag rgyas kyang mnan no //
NK011(da)003:1820: gong gi sa bcad drug pa zhal du stob pa ni bab brgyad kyis bskul lo //
NK011(da)003:1821: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dgra bgegs bin+d+ha ya bin+d+ha ya h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1822: ces ling ro rnams bdud rtsir sbyar ba zhal du stob cing /
NK011(da)003:1825: 'bar ba chen po'i zhal hom du //
NK011(da)003:1826: bstan pa 'jig pa'i dgra dang bgegs //
NK011(da)003:1827: ngas bstabs khyod kyis yud la rol //
NK011(da)003:1828: shin tu gdug cing gtum pa la //
NK011(da)003:1829: zhi bas phan par mi 'gyur bas //
NK011(da)003:1830: mi rtag mtshan nyid bstan pa'i phyir //
NK011(da)003:1831: za byed khro bo zhal phyes shig /
NK011(da)003:1832: lhag ma med par bzhes nas kyang //
NK011(da)003:1833: dgra bgegs bag chags kun sbyang ste //
NK011(da)003:1834: nam mkha'i khro bo za byed che'i //
NK011(da)003:1835: zhal gyi dbyings su stong khams thim //
NK011(da)003:1837: gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor na //
NK011(da)003:1838: bcom ldan dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu dang //
NK011(da)003:1839: gnyis med yum chen 'khor lo rgyas 'debs ma //
NK011(da)003:1840: ye shes thabs kyi sprul pa'i khro bo bcu //
NK011(da)003:1841: shes rab dbyings las shar ba'i khro mo bcu //
NK011(da)003:1842: za byed gsod byed phra men mche gshog tshogs //
NK011(da)003:1843: mthar byed chen mo ye shes sgo ma bzhi //
NK011(da)003:1844: gdug pa sgrol ba'i sras mchog phur bu'i tshogs //
NK011(da)003:1845: gnam sa gdangs pa lta bu'i zhal phye la //
NK011(da)003:1846: zla gam glog dmar 'khyug 'dra'i ljags brkyang ste //
NK011(da)003:1847: gangs ri'i phreng ba lta bu'i tshems 'dor la //
NK011(da)003:1848: bstan pa bshig pa'i dgra bgegs zhal du stob //
NK011(da)003:1849: zhal du bstab bo bzhes shig kha ram kh+aa hi //
NK011(da)003:1850: dkyil 'khor de yi phyi rol bar khyams na //
NK011(da)003:1851: dbang phyug chen po nyi shu rtsa brgyad dang //
NK011(da)003:1852: gsod pa'i las mdzad srung ma bcu gnyis dang //
NK011(da)003:1853: ging chen ging phran dge bsnyen nyer gcig sogs //
NK011(da)003:1854: phur pa'i srung mar zhal bzhes thams cad kyang //
NK011(da)003:1855: rngams pa'i zhal gdangs 'bar ba'i ljags brkyang ste //
NK011(da)003:1856: skye 'gro rtsad nas gcod pa'i tshems 'dor la //
NK011(da)003:1857: bstan pa 'jig pa'i dgra bgegs zhal du stob //
NK011(da)003:1858: zhal du bstab bo bzhes shig kha ram kh+aa hi //
NK011(da)003:1859: 'dod chags khrag la thib thib dgyes par rol //
NK011(da)003:1860: zhe sdang rus pa khrum khrum dgyes par rol //
NK011(da)003:1861: gti mug sha la chem chem dgyes par rol //
NK011(da)003:1862: nga rgyal mkhris pa'i phung po mchod par bzhes //
NK011(da)003:1863: phrag dog glo snying rol cig kha ram kh+aa hi //
NK011(da)003:1864: dug lnga bsgral ba'i mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK011(da)003:1865: sku gsung thugs dang yon tan phrin las kyi //
NK011(da)003:1866: dngos grub thams cad dus 'dir rtsal du gsol //
NK011(da)003:1867: badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)003:1868: ma h+aa m+aam sa kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)003:1871: ma h+aa ba su ta kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)003:1872: ma h+aa kem ni ri ti kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)003:1873: ma h+aa go ro tsa na kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)003:1875: bee d+aur sngon po'i rin chen ri rab la //
NK011(da)003:1876: nyi ma stong gi 'od zer gdal ba ltar //
NK011(da)003:1877: sems dpa' sngon po 'od kyi dkyil 'khor can //
NK011(da)003:1878: dpal ldan gzi brjid 'bar la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)003:1879: 'od phung stug po sprin ltar 'khrigs pa yi //
NK011(da)003:1880: 'jigs byed rngams stabs brkyangs bskum tshul du bzhugs //
NK011(da)003:1881: za byed bskal pa'i me ltar 'bar ba ste //
NK011(da)003:1882: gdug pa thams cad rdo rje'i zhal du 'dren //
NK011(da)003:1883: mi bzad mche ba gtsigs pa'i zhal gdangs shing //
NK011(da)003:1884: srid gsum za bar chas pa'i rkan sgra can //
NK011(da)003:1885: nyi zla rab tu 'bar ba'i sdang mig gis //
NK011(da)003:1886: bgegs dpung bsreg par mdzad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)003:1887: ces che ba'i yon tan gyis bstod //
NK011(da)003:1889: gsang sngags kyi byin gyis brlab pa'o //
NK011(da)003:1891: zhes chos nyid kyi bden pa brdar ro //
NK011(da)003:1892: lnga pa tshogs la rol pa ni /
NK011(da)003:1893: las kyi rdo rje rgyal po la phyag byas dza gad dang m+aam sa bsnol mar stob cing /
NK011(da)003:1894: tshogs kyi mchod pa rgyan du rol //
NK011(da)003:1896: a la la hoh zhes blangs la /
NK011(da)003:1897: 'og min lto ba'i gzhal yas su //
NK011(da)003:1898: dkyil 'khor lha rnams spyan drangs nas //
NK011(da)003:1899: ye shes chen po'i me sbar te //
NK011(da)003:1900: hom gzar lag pas mchod rdzas btab //
NK011(da)003:1901: ha ha hu lu bzhes su gsol //
NK011(da)003:1902: ces gsal btab la lha tshogs rnams mchod par bsam la rol lo //
NK011(da)003:1903: drug pa lhag ma'i cho ga ni /
NK011(da)003:1904: lhag ma rnams gsog 'jog med par bsdus pa dang /
NK011(da)003:1905: sngar gyi phud lhag bcas dkyil 'khor gyi shar lho dri yi man+dala gyi khar bzhag /
NK011(da)003:1906: slob dpon gyi lce la rta mgrin yab yum rol
NK011(da)003:1907: pa mdzad pa'i byang sems bdud rtsir bab par bsam
NK011(da)003:1908: pa / mkha' dbyings kyi rgyas dza gad kyi kha phru btab la /
NK011(da)003:1909: gu ru tra ha ka sa ma ya bag sha
NK011(da)003:1910: su gan su tri shi tri la tish+tha thangs la
NK011(da)003:1913: bcom ldan dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu yis //
NK011(da)003:1914: las kyi rdo rje byed par dbang bskur ba'i //
NK011(da)003:1915: lhag ma kha chu'i dam tshig mnga' mdzad rnams //
NK011(da)003:1916: dam tshig tshul bzhin mchod kyis gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)003:1917: rta mgrin gyi phyag rgyas dbang du bsdus la /
NK011(da)003:1918: dzahh+aum bam hoh badz+ra t+aa ki n+ai a kar+sha ya
NK011(da)003:1919: h+aum dzah e +aa ral+l+ai h+r+aim h+r+aim t+aa ki n+ai
NK011(da)003:1921: pra be sha ya pra be sha ya /
NK011(da)003:1923: to sha ya to sha ya /
NK011(da)003:1924: mo ha ya mo ha ya /
NK011(da)003:1925: sarba badz+ra t+aa ki n+ai n+aam h+r+ai da yam h+aum
NK011(da)003:1926: dzahdzahh+aum bam hoh d+aa ki n+ai h+aum dzah bdag nyid
NK011(da)003:1927: dpal chen po'i sku'i gzi byin gyi zil gyis mnan
NK011(da)003:1928: la / badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba dush+tam
NK011(da)003:1929: sa ma ya mu tra pra b+han tsakra ya bi
NK011(da)003:1930: ng+h+wa na sa ma ya hoh b+ha ga wa na
NK011(da)003:1931: b+hud+d+ha k+she tra pra t+aits+tsha ya h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1932: pad+ma pa ta pa mu kha /
NK011(da)003:1934: pra be sha ya pra be sha ya /
NK011(da)003:1936: to sha ya to sha ya /
NK011(da)003:1937: mo ha ya mo ha ya /
NK011(da)003:1938: sarba badz+ra t+aa ki n+ai n+aam h+r+ai da ya /
NK011(da)003:1941: mo +aahh+aum badz+ra d+aa ki n+ai pra t+aits+tsha mam ba lim ta h+aum phata /
NK011(da)003:1942: bud+d+ha d+aa ki n+ai pra t+aits+tsha mam ba lim ta phata /
NK011(da)003:1943: rat+na d+aa ki n+ai pra t+aits+tsha mam ba lim ta s+w+aa phata /
NK011(da)003:1944: pad+ma d+aa ki n+ai pra t+aits+tsha mam ba lim ta +aam phata /
NK011(da)003:1945: karma d+aa ki n+ai pra t+aits+tsha mam ba limta h+aa phata /
NK011(da)003:1948: gu ru kro d+ha rat+na sa ma ya p+r+ai sha
NK011(da)003:1949: pur+na k+she tra p+aa la k+sho b+ha ka ra h+aum
NK011(da)003:1952: rnam dag chos dbyings zhi ba las //
NK011(da)003:1953: thugs rje chen po'i sprul pa 'byung //
NK011(da)003:1954: thabs shes zla gsang thig le las //
NK011(da)003:1955: yal gam can rnams 'du bar mdzod //
NK011(da)003:1957: rdo rje nam mkhar 'gro ma rnams //
NK011(da)003:1958: yi dwags rta la yang dag zhon //
NK011(da)003:1959: gdug pa'i sems kyis sdig byed cing //
NK011(da)003:1960: dpa' bo brjid pa'i gzugs 'dzin pa //
NK011(da)003:1961: skal ldan rang gi lag char ldan //
NK011(da)003:1962: sha khrag dang ni rgyu ma dang //
NK011(da)003:1963: rkang dang tshil bu za zhing byon //
NK011(da)003:1964: mkha' 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis po //
NK011(da)003:1965: kun kyang smug nag ral gri dang //
NK011(da)003:1966: b+han+d+ha khrag bkang lag na thogs //
NK011(da)003:1967: ye shes las grub mkha' 'gro rnams //
NK011(da)003:1968: don gyi sangs rgyas yin mod kyang //
NK011(da)003:1969: sgrub pa po la phan gdags phyir //
NK011(da)003:1970: bran gyi tshul du khas blangs pa //
NK011(da)003:1971: sngon gyi thugs dam brtser dgongs la //
NK011(da)003:1972: 'dir gshegs mchod kyi phrin las mdzod //
NK011(da)003:1973: dpal chen tshogs kyi las byed pa //
NK011(da)003:1974: khro chen badz+ra king ka ra //
NK011(da)003:1975: khro mo khams gsum dbugs sdud bcas //
NK011(da)003:1976: tan gan phrin las dus la bab //
NK011(da)003:1977: sngo skya ral gri lcags kyu thogs //
NK011(da)003:1978: khams gsum sgrol ba'i ging bco brgyad //
NK011(da)003:1979: dam bcas bzhin du gshegs nas kyang //
NK011(da)003:1980: rnam lnga'i mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK011(da)003:1981: dgyes pa'i gar gyis phrin las mdzod //
NK011(da)003:1982: lha dbang brgya byin bu mo ste //
NK011(da)003:1983: 'bar ma nyi ma'i zhags pa sogs //
NK011(da)003:1984: 'bar ma chen mo brgyad rnams kyang //
NK011(da)003:1985: rang rang cha lugs dang ldan zhing //
NK011(da)003:1986: so so'i las rnams bsgos pa ste //
NK011(da)003:1987: dam bcas bzhin du ma g.yel bar //
NK011(da)003:1988: bka' yi gtor ma 'di longs la //
NK011(da)003:1989: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK011(da)003:1990: pho nya chen mo thams cad kyang //
NK011(da)003:1991: shel mchong bse yi ma mo dang //
NK011(da)003:1992: g.yu lcags gser gi ma mo ste //
NK011(da)003:1993: pho nya sum brgya drug cu rnams //
NK011(da)003:1994: bye ba phrag khrig 'khor dang bcas //
NK011(da)003:1995: bka' yi gtor ma 'di longs la //
NK011(da)003:1996: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK011(da)003:1997: rdo rje kun grags la sogs pa'i //
NK011(da)003:1998: brtan ma chen mo bcu gnyis po //
NK011(da)003:1999: rang rang 'khor g.yog dpung dang bcas //
NK011(da)003:2000: kun kyang nag mo ral pa can //
NK011(da)003:2002: nag mo ral gri thod khrag 'dzin //
NK011(da)003:2003: gser sbrul mang po'i khri steng nas //
NK011(da)003:2004: dam tshig can la brtser dgongs nas //
NK011(da)003:2005: mchod pa dam pa 'di bzhes la //
NK011(da)003:2006: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK011(da)003:2007: gling bzhi mgyogs ma lha yi sring //
NK011(da)003:2008: mkha' la khyung lding gshin rje'i sring //
NK011(da)003:2009: dmar mo g.yag thod klu yi sring //
NK011(da)003:2010: nag mo sder can gnod sbyin sring //
NK011(da)003:2011: sring mo bzhi po gnas 'dir byon //
NK011(da)003:2012: dam skongs mchod do phrin las mdzod //
NK011(da)003:2013: dbang phyug chen mo nyi shu brgyad //
NK011(da)003:2014: snying rje byams pa'i spyod yul can //
NK011(da)003:2015: tshangs ma la sogs ma sring tshogs //
NK011(da)003:2016: bran dang yang bran 'khor dang bcas //
NK011(da)003:2017: dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu yi //
NK011(da)003:2018: bka' yi gtor ma 'di longs la //
NK011(da)003:2019: da lta khyod kyi gzugs mchog rnams //
NK011(da)003:2020: mngon du bstan la dngos grub phul //
NK011(da)003:2021: ji srid dngos grub ma phul bar //
NK011(da)003:2022: khyod rnams mngon par ma gyur cig /
NK011(da)003:2023: bar du brten pa'i gnas 'di ru //
NK011(da)003:2024: 'dug la las rnams kun gyis shig /
NK011(da)003:2025: ma mo chen mo khyed rnams kyis //
NK011(da)003:2026: sngon tshe dpal chen he ru ka'i //
NK011(da)003:2027: spyan sngar khas blangs dam bcas bzhin //
NK011(da)003:2029: ye shes thob par bya ba'i phyir //
NK011(da)003:2030: sgrub pa po yi las bya zhes //
NK011(da)003:2031: dam las ma 'da' phrin las mdzod //
NK011(da)003:2032: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)003:2034: ma h+aa ba lim ng+ta kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)003:2035: zhes mchod cing sman raka sbreng la /
NK011(da)003:2036: hoh lhag sdud kyi dam tshig la gtogs pa'i mkha'
NK011(da)003:2037: 'gro dam can rgya mtsho'i tshogs 'khor dang bcas pa
NK011(da)003:2038: rnams lha ma'i dam tshig 'dis tshim zhing dgyes par
NK011(da)003:2039: gyur te / dam tshig nyams chag thams cad skongs nas sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa srungs /
NK011(da)003:2041: dge 'dun dang chos kyi rgyal srid skyongs /
NK011(da)003:2043: sems can gyi phan bde spel /
NK011(da)003:2044: rnam 'byor ba rnams kyi sdong grogs mdzod /
NK011(da)003:2045: sngags 'chang rnams kyi phrin las sgrubs /
NK011(da)003:2046: khyad par dam tshig 'dir 'dus pa rnams kyi phyi nang gsang ba'i 'gal rkyen zhi ba dang /
NK011(da)003:2047: mchog thun mong gi dngos grub ma lus pa myur du 'grub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK011(da)003:2049: ya hi gats+tshasa mgron rnams rang gnas su gshegs par
NK011(da)003:2050: bsams la gtor ma phyir dor nas ma man+dala bsdu'o
NK011(da)003:2051: // bdun pa brtan ma skyong ba ni /
NK011(da)003:2052: phyi rol du brtan ma'i gtor ma phud kyis bran la /
NK011(da)003:2053: tram rat+na tree lo kya phata /
NK011(da)003:2054: gtor ma'i rdul phra rab re re bzhin rin po
NK011(da)003:2055: che'i gur khang longs spyod zad mi shes pas nam
NK011(da)003:2059: tshogs dang bka' yi tshogs bcas nyid //
NK011(da)003:2060: khrag 'thung de bzhin nam mkha'i sku //
NK011(da)003:2061: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs skyong ma rnams //
NK011(da)003:2062: 'dir spyon dam skongs phrin las mdzod //
NK011(da)003:2063: bdag nyid chen mo la sogs bdud mo bzhi //
NK011(da)003:2064: gangs dkar sha med la sogs gnod sbyin bzhi //
NK011(da)003:2065: kong btsun de mo la sogs sman mo bzhi //
NK011(da)003:2066: bod khams skyong ba'i che zhe chen mo rnams //
NK011(da)003:2067: bran g.yog mang po'i 'khor dang bcas //
NK011(da)003:2068: lhab lhub mang po'i rgyan dang bcas //
NK011(da)003:2069: sil snyan mang po'i sgra dang bcas //
NK011(da)003:2070: 'dir spyon dam skongs phrin las mdzod //
NK011(da)003:2071: che zhe chen mo khyed rnams kyang //
NK011(da)003:2072: a su ra yi brag phug tu //
NK011(da)003:2074: rlangs chen dpal gyi seg ge yis //
NK011(da)003:2075: zhing chen stan la bkod nas kyang //
NK011(da)003:2076: rdo rje lag tu gtad nas ni //
NK011(da)003:2077: dbang bskur gsang ba'i mtshan nas brjod //
NK011(da)003:2078: rdo rje 'chang gi gral du bzhag /
NK011(da)003:2079: bod khams bsrung zhing skyong ba dang //
NK011(da)003:2080: rnal 'byor sgrub pa'i grogs bya zhes //
NK011(da)003:2081: ji ltar khas blangs dam bcas pa'i //
NK011(da)003:2082: g.yar dam gnyan po rjes dgongs la //
NK011(da)003:2083: dam rdzas bka' yi gtor ma longs //
NK011(da)003:2084: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK011(da)003:2085: la la le le tam tam te te kha rak+ma ma ma sring 'gro ma h+aum b+h+yo h+aum h+aum /
NK011(da)003:2087: ma h+aa pany+tsa sogs sman raka gtor gsum gyis mchod cing /
NK011(da)003:2089: brtan ma bcu gnyis 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyis
NK011(da)003:2090: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa srungs sogs kyis phrin las
NK011(da)003:2091: bcol nas / ya hi gats+tshasa gshegs su gsol nas gtor ma gtsang sar bskyal lo //
NK011(da)003:2092: brgyad pa las bzhi'i bro brdung ba ni /
NK011(da)003:2093: gtor gzhong ri rab tu gyur pa'i 'og tu dam sri bkug nas mnan par bsam la /
NK011(da)003:2095: sangs rgyas kun gyi sku gsung thugs //
NK011(da)003:2096: gti mug bde gshegs 'khor bcas rnams //
NK011(da)003:2097: de bzhin rigs mchog ma lus kyis //
NK011(da)003:2099: shin tu rmongs pa'i sems can rnams //
NK011(da)003:2100: zhi ba thugs rje chen po yis //
NK011(da)003:2101: zhi bar ma gyur gang yang med //
NK011(da)003:2102: zhi mdzad lha la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)003:2103: sh+ain+tam ku ru ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK011(da)003:2104: sangs rgyas kun gyi sku gsung thugs //
NK011(da)003:2105: nga rgyal bde gshegs 'khor bcas rnams //
NK011(da)003:2106: rin chen rigs mchog ma lus kyis //
NK011(da)003:2108: shin tu dregs pa'i sems can kun //
NK011(da)003:2109: tshe dbang dngos grub rgyas mdzad pas //
NK011(da)003:2110: rgyas par ma gyur gang yang med //
NK011(da)003:2111: rgyas mdzad lha la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)003:2113: sangs rgyas kun gyi sku gsung thugs //
NK011(da)003:2115: pad+ma rigs mchog ma lus kyis //
NK011(da)003:2117: shin tu chags pa'i sems can rnams //
NK011(da)003:2118: yud tsam gyis ni bsdu mdzad pas //
NK011(da)003:2119: dbang du ma gyur gang yang med //
NK011(da)003:2120: dbang mdzad lha la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)003:2121: p+aa sham ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK011(da)003:2122: sangs rgyas kun gyi sku gsung thugs //
NK011(da)003:2123: zhe sdang bde gshegs 'khor bcas rnams //
NK011(da)003:2124: rdo rje'i rigs mchog ma lus kyis //
NK011(da)003:2126: shin tu gdug pa'i sems can rnams //
NK011(da)003:2127: yud tsam gyis ni bsdus nas kyang //
NK011(da)003:2128: rdul du ma brlag gang yang med //
NK011(da)003:2129: brlag mdzad lha la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)003:2130: ces las bzhi'i bro dang h+aum bzhi pa'i mthar m+aa ra ya phata /
NK011(da)003:2131: dgu pa dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK011(da)003:2133: rdo rje phur pa'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs dgongs //
NK011(da)003:2134: sku gsung thugs dang yon tan phrin las kyi //
NK011(da)003:2135: byin rlabs dbang dang dngos grub ma lus pa //
NK011(da)003:2136: da lta nyid du bdag la stsal du gsol //
NK011(da)003:2137: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba sid+d+hi pha la hoh bcu pa bzod par gsol ba ni /
NK011(da)003:2138: hoh bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje gzhon nu'i lha
NK011(da)003:2139: tshogs 'khor dang bcas pa thams cad bdag la dgongs
NK011(da)003:2140: su gsol / bdag cag so so'i skye bor gyur pas nyon mongs pa can du gyur nas /
NK011(da)003:2141: lus ngag yid gsum gyi spyod pa nyon mongs pa dang 'dres te bag med par gyur pa dang /
NK011(da)003:2142: rnal 'byor pa dbang ma thob pa dang bying ba dang rgod pa'i dbang du gyur te /
NK011(da)003:2143: ting nge 'dzin mi gsal ba dang /
NK011(da)003:2144: le lo'i dbang du gyur nas mchod rdzas ma 'byor pa dang /
NK011(da)003:2145: shes bzhin ma rig pa'i dbang du gyur nas cho
NK011(da)003:2146: ga lhag chad du gyur pa dang ser sna'i dbang
NK011(da)003:2147: gis mchod pa ngan zhing chung ba dang /
NK011(da)003:2148: gti mug gi dbang gis rgyud sde nas byung ba'i
NK011(da)003:2149: cho ga ci bzhin ma lcogs pa sogs 'gal 'khrul
NK011(da)003:2150: nongs pa ci mchis pa thams bzod par bzhes nas
NK011(da)003:2151: / bdag cag gi lam dang dngos grub kyi bar
NK011(da)003:2152: chad du mi 'gyur bar byin gyis brlab par mdzad
NK011(da)003:2153: / du gsol lo // zhes gsol zhing yi ge brgya pa brjod do //
NK011(da)003:2154: bcu gcig pa nyer bsdu ni /
NK011(da)003:2156: zhes brjod pas dkyil 'khor gsum gyi lha rnams h+aum yig gsum du gyur /
NK011(da)003:2158: de las 'od 'phros te don gnyis byas tshur 'dus h+aum yig gsum la thim /
NK011(da)003:2159: gnyis po bdag nyid rtsa ba'i h+aum la thim /
NK011(da)003:2160: h+aum gyen rdzogs thig ler yal ba'i ngang du mi dmigs par bzhag pas rtag mtha' bsal lo //
NK011(da)003:2161: bcu gnyis pa rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK011(da)003:2162: stong nyid de'i ngang nas h+aum h+aum zhes pas h+aum yig sbrel mar gyur /
NK011(da)003:2163: de las 'od zer 'phros 'dus nas h+aum yig gnyis
NK011(da)003:2164: rdo rje gzhon nu yab yum gyi skur gyur pa'i
NK011(da)003:2165: spyi bor zla ba'i steng du ha yig gis mtshan
NK011(da)003:2166: par bsam la / rdo rje rgya gram gyi phyag rgya bcings te /
NK011(da)003:2167: badz+ra k+aa w+aa tsi rak+sha ham /
NK011(da)003:2169: lus rdo rje'i go khrab kyi zhu lugs su g.yogs par blta'o //
NK011(da)003:2170: mdzub mo gnyis la nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor re re'i
NK011(da)003:2171: steng du rdo rje gnod sbyin sngon po mche ba
NK011(da)003:2172: dang / bdud rtsi thab sbyor dmar po rgya gram bsnams par mos te /
NK011(da)003:2173: lte ba snying ga ltag pa dpral ba spyi bo ste gnas lngar /
NK011(da)003:2174: trum zhes brjod bzhin par mdzub mo gnyis bsnol te
NK011(da)003:2175: rim par reg pas khro bo gnyis rgyab sprad de
NK011(da)003:2176: bzhugs nas bsrung zhing brtan par bya'o //
NK011(da)003:2177: rin po che'i phyag rgya mgo bo'i gnas lngar bzhag la /
NK011(da)003:2178: rat+na mu ku tram zhes rin po ches dbu brgyan par bsam /
NK011(da)003:2179: tush+ya hoh zhes dgyes pas thal mo gdab cing /
NK011(da)003:2180: dar dmar mthing gis dbang bskur bar mos la /
NK011(da)003:2181: yi ge brgya ba lan gsum bzlas pas brtan par bya'o //
NK011(da)003:2182: bcu gsum pa bsngo smon ni /
NK011(da)003:2183: dge ba 'di yis bdag dang sems can kun //
NK011(da)003:2184: bdud las rnam rgyal bar chad kun zhi zhing //
NK011(da)003:2185: rdo rje gzhon nu mya ngan 'das pa'i sar //
NK011(da)003:2186: 'bras bu byang chub nges par brnyes gyur cig /
NK011(da)003:2188: bcu bzhi pa bkra shis brjod pa ni /
NK011(da)003:2190: byin rlabs mchog stsol rtsa brgyud bla ma dang //
NK011(da)003:2191: dngos grub char 'bebs rdo rje gzhon nu che //
NK011(da)003:2192: khro bcu sras mchog sgo srung dam can sogs //
NK011(da)003:2193: rab 'byams dkyil 'khor 'khor lo'i bkra shis shog /
NK011(da)003:2194: ces brjod pas mtha' rgyas par bya'o //
NK011(da)003:2195: de yang spyod lam rgyun gyi rnal 'byor ni /
NK011(da)003:2196: snod kyi 'jig rten thams cad rdo rje phur pa'i gzhal yas khang /
NK011(da)003:2197: bcud kyi sems can thams cad rdo rje gzhon nu yab yum /
NK011(da)003:2198: sgrar grags pa thams cad k+ai la ya'i rang sgra /
NK011(da)003:2199: sems kyi dran rtog thams cad stong gsal rjen pa
NK011(da)003:2200: rdo rje gzhon nu'i thugs su lam du 'khyer ba
NK011(da)003:2201: la bslab par bya ba yin no //
NK011(da)003:2202: de ltar dpal chen rdo rje phur bu yi //
NK011(da)003:2203: las gzhung o rgyan chen po'i rtsa ba la //
NK011(da)003:2204: brten cing jo mo lcam dang skye khyud dang //
NK011(da)003:2205: lang lab sna nam mkhas pa rong zom gyi //
NK011(da)003:2206: gzhung las legs bsdus dngos grub rgya mtsho zhes //
NK011(da)003:2207: tshig don legs bshad nyin mor byed pa'i dpal //
NK011(da)003:2208: byin rlabs 'od stong 'phro 'di mkhas pa dang //
NK011(da)003:2209: grub pa'i gtsug rgyan blo gros rgyal mtshan gyis //
NK011(da)003:2210: mdzad pa'i las byang yid bzhin rin chen dang //
NK011(da)003:2211: mtshungs pa de las legs bsdus bris pa'i dges //
NK011(da)003:2212: ma rung bdud sde'i g.yul las rnam rgyal te //
NK011(da)003:2213: rdo rje gzhon nu'i go 'phang myur thob shog /
NK011(da)003:2214: ces phur bu'i las byang dngos grub rgya mtsho'i snying po zhes bya ba 'di ni /
NK011(da)003:2215: dpon slob mnga' bdag brag rig 'dzin rgya mtshos don
NK011(da)003:2216: gnyer chen pos mthun pa'i rkyen sbyar te o rgyan
NK011(da)003:2217: smin grol gling 'dus sder 'di nyid kyi chog grwa
NK011(da)003:2218: 'dzugs par mdzad pa'i tshe las byang khyer bde ba
NK011(da)003:2219: zhig dgos zhes so ston mthu stobs rnam rgyal sogs
NK011(da)003:2221: nye char rang gi gam du 'khod pa'i mi pham gyis kha btags dang go dmar kha /
NK011(da)003:2222: chos dbyings kyis kha btags kyi rten dang bcas yang yang gsol btab pa la brten /
NK011(da)003:2223: rin chen rnam par rgyal ba'i ming can gyis bris
NK011(da)003:2224: pa ste dpe dpang dag pa zhig ma rnyed pas
NK011(da)003:2225: sngags sogs la dpyad gzhi 'ga' re mchis pas slar
NK011(da)003:2226: ma phyi'i dpe nyid khung btsun rnyed na mkhas pa
NK011(da)003:2227: rnams kyis dpyad par mdzod cig /
